is%20%24267%2C230%20loan.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222882%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Clarence%20Thomas%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F642efaeec328830019d9f259%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221441%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESupreme%20Court%20Justice%20Clarence%20Thomas.%3Cp%3ESaul%20Loeb%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EA%20Senate%20committee%20found%20that%20Clarence%20Thomas%20had%20a%20substantial%20loan%20forgiven%20by%20a%20wealthy%20friend%20in%202008.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThomas'%20friend%2C%20healthcare%20exec%20Anthony%20Welters%2C%20loaned%20him%20over%20%24260%2C000%20that%20Thomas%20used%20to%20purchase%20a%20luxury%20RV.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20findings%20came%20four%20months%20after%20Thomas%20joined%20a%20majority%20Supreme%20Court%20opinion%20striking%20down%20Biden's%20student%20debt%20forgiveness%20plan.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESupreme%20Court%20Justice%20Clarence%20Thomas%20ruled%20this%20year%20that%20Joe%20Biden%20was%20wrong%20when%20he%20tried%20to%20forgive%20college%20students'%20loans%2C%20but%20a%20Senate%20panel%20revealed%20that%20Thomas%20had%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclarence-thomas-luxury-rv-loan-forgiven-anthony-welters-senate-inquiry-2023-10%5C%22%3Esubstantial%20loan%20of%20his%20own%20forgiven%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20a%20wealthy%20friend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThomas%20joined%20a%20majority%20opinion%20in%20June%20that%20struck%20down%20the%20White%20House's%20student%20debt%20relief%20plan%20and%20found%20Biden%20overstepped%20his%20authority.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20two%20months%20later%20%E2%80%94%20as%20ethics%20questions%20swirled%20around%20the%20conservative%20justice%20over%20his%20cozy%20relationship%20with%20rich%20friends%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F08%2F05%2Fus%2Fclarence-thomas-rv-anthony-welters.html%5C%22%3Et