nologies%20such%20as%20robotic%20process%20automation%2C%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20and%20machine%20learning%20are%20streamlining%20the%20workload%20of%20retail-supply-chain%20workers%2C%20Maguire%20said.%20Amazon%2C%20for%20example%2C%20has%20developed%20and%20deployed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-robot-arm-sparrow-replace-human-warehouse-workers-2022-11%5C%22%3Ea%20robot%20that%20can%20perform%20simple%20tasks%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20its%20fulfillment%20centers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aboutamazon.com%2Fnews%2Foperations%2Famazon-introduces-sparrow-a-state-of-the-art-robot-that-handles-millions-of-diverse-products%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ee-commerce%20giant%20says%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20robot%20%26quot%3Bstreamlines%20the%20fulfillment%20process%20by%20moving%20individual%20products%20before%20they%20get%20packaged%26quot%3B%20and%20even%20brands%20it%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bmajor%20technological%20advancement%26quot%3B%20for%20its%20staff.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20Amazon%20employees%20are%20concerned%20that%20this%20technology%20will%20eventually%20take%20over%20their%20jobs.%20But%20Maguire's%20view%20is%20that%20it'll%20help%20workers%20%26quot%3Bdiversify%20their%20skills%2C%20work%20faster%2C%20and%20evolve%20with%20the%20market%20changes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BTechnology%20will%20merely%20act%20as%20a%20support%20pillar%2C%20enhancing%20human%20capabilities%2C%20rather%20than%20replacing%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20innovations%20will%20%26quot%3Bcontinue%20to%20bolster%20and%20streamline%20the%20retail%20supply%20chain%20as%20they%20become%20even%20more%20sophisticated%2C%26quot%3B%20Maguire%20said.%20Use%20cases%20for%20AI%20and%20machine%20learning%20include%20predicting%20product%20demand%20and%20optimizing%20inventory.%20This%20is%20possible%20with%20the%20analysis%20of%20factors%20such%20as%20past%20sales%2C%20promotions%2C%20economic%20indicators%2C%20and%20seasonality%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERetail%20firms%20also%20use%20AI%20and%20machine%20learning%20to%20streamline%20the%20way%20they%20manage%20stock.%20Maguire%20said%20these%20innovations%20have%20helped%20retailers%20%26quot%3Bautomatically%20adjust%20reorder%20points%20and%20quantities%20based%20on%20real-time%20data%2C%20preventing%20overstock%20or%20understock%20situations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20technologies%20even%20allow%20retailers%20to%20set%20product%20prices%20based%20on%20rapid%20market%20changes%2C%20Maguire%20added.%20Doing%20so%20can%20help%20them%20increase%20profits%2C%20improve%20competitive%20advantage%2C%20and%20prevent%20overstock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ETech%20is%20key%20to%20addressing%20supply-chain%20challenges%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20navigating%20fast-changing%20retail%20trends%20and%20customer-purchasing%20behaviors%2C%20the%20retail%20supply%20chain%20has%20been%20heavily%20influenced%20by%20%26quot%3Bunprecedented%20challenges%26quot%3B%20in%20recent%20years%20such%20as%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20rising%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20disruptions%20have%20been%20coupled%20with%20a%20significant%20shortage%20of%20labor%2C%20leaving%20many%20logistics%20providers%20lacking%20the%20resources%20to%20facilitate%20warehouse%20operations%20and%20deliveries%2C%26quot%3B%20John%20Perry%2C%20the%20managing%20director%20at%20the%20supply-chain%20and%20logistics%20consultancy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scalagroup.co.uk%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESCALA%20Consulting%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20survive%2C%20Perry%20said%20that%20the%20retail%20supply%20chain%20must%20take%20steps%20to%20become%20more%20agile%20and%20flexible.%20One%20way%20to%20do%20this%20is%20by%20leveraging%20robotics%20and%20other%20automations%20to%20develop%20%26quot%3Bresilient%20systems%20that%20can%20withstand%20challenges%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22711%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Headshot%20of%20John%20Perry%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653a70f096f7540cd06657af%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22711%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJohn%20Perry%2C%20the%20managing%20director%20at%20SCALA%20Consulting.%3Cp%3ESCALA%20Consulting%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECiting%20a%20survey%20from%20SCALA%2C%20he%20said%20many%20companies%20were%20investing%20in%20these%20technologies%20to%20%26quot%3Bmake%20their%20supply%20chains%20more%20efficient%20and%20flexible.%26quot%3B%20In%20the%20survey%2C%2035%25%20of%20respondents%20said%20they%20had%20invested%20between%20about%20%241.2%20million%20and%20%246%20million%2C%20while%20an%20impressive%2028%25%20said%20they'd%20invested%20more%20than%20that.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20those%20already%20utilizing%20the%20technology%2C%20many%20have%20already%20felt%20a%20substantial%20impact%2C%26quot%3B%20Perry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20common%20benefits%20of%20using%20robotics%20and%20automation%20are%20greater%20productivity%2C%20better%20ability%20to%20meet%20customer%20demand%2C%20and%20cost%20savings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENaji%20El-Arifi%2C%20the%20head%20of%20innovation%20at%20communications%20agency%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wundermanthompson.com%2Fexpertise%2Fcommerce%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWunderman%20Thompson%20Commerce%20%26amp%3B%20Technology%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20that%20AI%20was%20a%20useful%20tool%20for%20retailers%20wanting%20to%20cut%20costs%20and%20boost%20efficiencies%20in%20their%20supply%20chains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20the%20British%20furniture%20retailer%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dfs.co.uk%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDFS%3C%2Fa%3E%20uses%20this%20technology%20to%20help%20its%20delivery%20drivers%20quickly%20determine%20the%20most%20efficient%20delivery%20routes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20has%20meant%20drivers%20can%20make%20more%20drop-offs%2C%20all%20while%20using%20as%20little%20fuel%20as%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20El-Arifi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221571%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Headshot%20of%20Naji%20El-Arifi%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653a729c356802a56be48bad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221571%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENaji%20El-Arifi%2C%20the%20head%20of%20innovation%20at%20the%20communications%20agency%20Wunderman%20Thompson%20Commerce%20%26amp%3B%20Technology.%3Cp%3EWunderman%20Thompson%20Commerce%20%26amp%3B%20Technology%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3ETracking%20stock%20with%20big%20data%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20challenge%20many%20retailers%20face%20is%20tracking%20large%20volumes%20of%20products%20stored%20in%20their%20warehouses.%20This%20can%20lead%20to%20issues%20such%20as%20overstocking%20and%20product%20wastage%2C%20said%20Samuel%20Mueller%2C%20the%20CEO%20and%20cofounder%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scandit.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EScandit%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20tech%20company%20that%20provides%20software%20for%20smart%20data%20capture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToo%20much%20stock%20is%20stored%20in%20back-of-house%20environments%2C%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20it%20can't%20be%20optimized%2C%20and%20workers%20take%20what%20they%20see%20first%2C%20rather%20than%20what%20might%20expire%20first%2C%20taking%20grocery%20as%20an%20example%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20by%20collecting%20stockroom%20data%20via%20smartphones%20and%20analyzing%20it%20with%20computer%20software%2C%20retailers%20can%20overcome%20these%20issues%20and%20ultimately%20make%20better%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDigital%20transformation%20through%20the%20use%20of%20AI%20as%20well%20as%20by%20capturing%20and%20accessing%20the%20right%20data%20via%20computer%20vision%20can%20overcome%20such%20challenges%20and%20enable%20more%20accurate%20forecasting%2C%26quot%3B%20Mueller%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221418%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Headshot%20of%20Samuel%20Mueller%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653a74fb0487ff031caf136d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221418%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESamuel%20Mueller%2C%20the%20CEO%20and%20a%20cofounder%20of%20Scandit.%3Cp%3EScandit%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3EA%20data-driven%20tech%20strategy%20can%20also%20help%20retailers%20appeal%20to%20sustainability-conscious%20consumers.%20For%20instance%2C%20many%20brands%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.just-style.com%2Fnews%2Fnobodys-child-line-at-asos-john-lewis-ms-uses-digital-product-passports%2F%3Fcf-view%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eusing%3C%2Fa%3E%20digital%20passports%20for%20collecting%20and%20sharing%20information%20illustrating%20a%20product's%20life%20span%20and%20environmental%20impact.%20This%20data%20can%20often%20be%20accessed%20by%20scanning%20a%20QR%20code%20on%20product%20tags%2C%20allowing%20customers%20to%20check%20whether%20an%20item%20is%20eco-friendly.%C2%A0%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20retailers%2C%20this%20enables%20them%20to%20monitor%20stock%20levels%20still%20left%20in%20the%20market%2C%20enhance%20their%20sustainability%20credentials%2C%20and%20get%20a%20slice%20of%20the%20pie%2C%20rather%20than%20leaving%20this%20'forgotten'%20market%20to%20third-party%20marketplaces%2C%26quot%3B%20Mueller%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20retailers%20can%20get%20the%20most%20out%20of%20supply-chain%20tech%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EApplying%20digital%20technology%20to%20traditional%20supply%20chains%20is%20a%20daunting%20prospect%20for%20many%20retailers%2C%20but%20retail%20experts%20said%20a%20few%20strategic%20moves%20could%20ease%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20retailers%20looking%20to%20invest%20in%20robotics%20and%20automation%2C%20Perry's%20advice%20is%20to%20analyze%20the%20processes%20in%20their%20supply%20chains%20and%20set%20quantifiable%20objectives.%20This%20helps%20them%20determine%20the%20areas%20that%20need%20digitization%20and%20%26quot%3Bguide%20the%20implementation%20process%20that%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20may%20happen%20over%20several%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20retailers%20adopt%20new%20technologies%2C%20employee%20training%20will%20also%20be%20crucial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRobotics%20and%20automation%20are%20not%20something%20employees%20should%20fear%2C%20so%20engaging%20them%20in%20the%20entire%20process%20will%20build%20trust%20and%20encourage%20them%20to%20use%20the%20systems%2C%26quot%3B%20Perry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaguire%20said%20companies%20should%20%26quot%3Bgain%20visibility%20across%20their%20supply-chain%20networks%20and%20shopping%20platforms%26quot%3B%20as%20they%20bolster%20tech%20initiatives.%20This%2C%20he%20said%2C%20involves%20%26quot%3Busing%20cutting-edge%20technologies%20to%20build%20a%20holistic%20view%20of%20their%20operations%2C%20monitor%20the%20evolving%20landscape%2C%20and%20identify%20areas%20for%20continuous%20improvement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-machine-learning-robotics-retail-supply-chain-technology-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698352027000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653a6a1f96f7540cd0664e3f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-machine-learning-robotics-retail-supply-chain-technology-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AI%2C%20machine%20learning%2C%20and%20robotics%20are%20improving%20retail%20supply%20chains.%20They%20help%20with%20productivity%2C%20production%20costs%2C%20meeting%20consumer%20demand%2C%20and%20more.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Nicholas%20Fearn)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A98%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-machine-learning-robotics-retail-supply-chain-technology-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%20a%20business%20and%20leadership%20coach%20who%20uses%20the%20Enneagram.%20I've%20had%20corporate%20clients%20cry%20during%20workshops.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side%20by%20side%20of%20a%20photo%20of%20Jay%20Hidalgo%20and%20a%20photo%20of%20the%20Enneagram%20circle%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6539bbde356802a56be453b6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJay%20Hidalgo%20uses%20the%20Enneagram%20in%20his%20leadership%20and%20business%20coaching%20practice.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jay%20Hidalgo%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJay%20Hidalgo%20is%20a%20business%20and%20leadership%20coach%20who%20uses%20the%20Enneagram%20in%20his%20corporate%20practice.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Enneagram%20is%20a%20personality%20model%20that%20characterizes%20people%20into%20one%20of%20nine%20archetypes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHidalgo%20said%20the%20Enneagram%20is%20a%20great%20tool%20for%20building%20team%20cohesion%20and%20addressing%20work%20conflict.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjayhidalgo.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EJay%20Hidalgo%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20a%20business%20and%20leadership%20coach%20who%20leads%20Enneagram%20trainings%20and%20workshops%20with%20corporate%20clients.%20The%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fwhat-is-enneagram-personality-type-number-meaning-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEnneagram%20is%20a%20personality%20model%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20that%20categorizes%20people%20into%20one%20of%20nine%20interconnected%20archetypes%20that%20are%20represented%20by%20numbers%20that%20attempt%20to%20explain%20people's%20characters%20through%20their%20core%20motivations%2C%20desires%2C%20and%20fears.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20ten%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20launched%20my%20firm%20with%20the%20desire%20to%20help%20executives%20become%20better%20leaders%2C%20build%20better%20teams%2C%20and%20build%20better%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20around%20the%20time%20I%20started%20my%20current%20firm%2C%20I%20was%20sitting%20in%20a%20coffee%20shop%20with%20a%20colleague%20and%20she%20told%20me%20about%20this%20thing%20called%20the%20Enneagram.%20I%20thought%20it%20sounded%20silly.%20There's%20no%20science%20behind%20it.%20It's%20all%20based%20on%20tradition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BOkay%2C%20that's%20nice.%20Maybe%20I'll%20look%20into%20it%20someday.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20a%20year%20later%2C%20one%20of%20the%20organizations%20I%20was%20working%20with%20asked%20me%20if%20I%20knew%20about%20the%20Enneagram.%20For%20whatever%20reason%2C%20the%20way%20they%20explained%20it%20landed%20with%20me%20and%20I%20started%20exploring%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20read%20about%20it%20and%20went%20and%20got%20myself%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.enneagraminstitute.com%2Ftype-descriptions%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etyped%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I'm%20an%20Enneagram%20six%20with%20a%20five%20wing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20through%20some%20certification%20and%20formal%20training%20on%20it.%20I%20came%20upon%20an%20Enneagram%20coach%20named%20Beth%20McCord%20and%20started%20reading%20her%20material.%20She%20offered%20a%20certification%20process%20that%20really%20landed%20with%20me.%20I%20got%20licensed%20through%20her%20material.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20I%20got%20interested%20in%20it%2C%20the%20more%20it%20started%20helping%20me%20understand%20myself%20better%20and%20helping%20me%20interact%20with%20the%20people%20around%20me%2C%20primarily%20my%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20mentioned%20it%20to%20one%20of%20my%20largest%20clients%20one%20day%2C%20a%20gentleman%20who%20has%20about%2030%20people%20directly%20underneath%20him.%20I%20asked%20him%20if%20he%20had%20ever%20heard%20of%20the%20Enneagram.%20We%20started%20talking%20about%20it%20and%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BDo%20you%20think%20you%20could%20teach%20this%20to%20our%20team%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20very%20confidently%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BSure.%20I%20think%20we%20could%20do%20a%20one-year%20program.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20to%20scurry%20behind%20the%20scenes%20and%20take%20what%20I%20was%20learning%20and%20convert%20it%20into%20a%20coaching%20methodology.%20But%20it%20was%20very%2C%20very%20successful%2C%20such%20that%20they%20decided%20to%20do%20it%20a%20second%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20eventually%20fostered%20it%20into%20becoming%20an%20offering%20in%20my%20firm.%20I've%20rolled%20it%20out%20to%20several%20clients%20since.%20It's%20been%20about%20six%20or%20seven%20years%20that%20we've%20been%20using%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Enneagram%20makes%20up%20about%2025%25%20of%20my%20firm's%20work%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20offer%20two%20workshops%3A%20half%20day%20is%20%244%2C500%20and%20full%20day%20is%20%247%2C500.%20The%20content%20is%20customizable%20based%20on%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20it's%20through%20a%20conversation%2C%20workshop%2C%20or%20coaching%20engagement%2C%20we've%20done%20it%20with%20financial%20service%20companies%3B%20we've%20done%20it%20with%20manufacturing%20groups%20and%20technology%20companies.%20I%20have%20one%20client%20who%20is%20a%20food%20manufacturer%20in%20New%20Jersey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20doesn't%20matter%20what%20they%20do%20or%20how%20they%20operate%20or%20what%20industry%20they're%20in.%20The%20Enneagram%20comes%20up%20when%20two%20primary%20needs%20emerge%20in%20conversation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20is%20when%20someone%20is%20really%20seeking%20to%20understand%20themselves%20as%20a%20leader.%20That%20will%20foster%20a%20conversation%20about%20their%20hard%20wiring%20and%20why%20they%20do%20what%20they%20do%20and%20think%20the%20way%20they%20think.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20thread%20of%20conversation%20is%20around%20team%20cohesion.%20The%20Enneagram%20is%20a%20fantastic%20tool%20for%20me%2C%20not%20only%20to%20understand%20myself%2C%20but%20also%20to%20understand%20my%20teammates.%20I%20can%20approach%20them%20in%20a%20different%20way%20when%20I%20understand%20their%20core%20underpinning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224933%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20blurred%20photo%20of%20a%20workplace%20meeting%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6539be2c96f7540cd06620c0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223283%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHidalgo%20told%20Insider%20he's%20been%20using%20the%20Enneagram%20in%20his%20workplace%20trainings%20for%20six%20or%20seven%20years.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20give%20our%20clients%20an%20overview%20of%20the%20Enneagram%20to%20start%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20session%20starts%2C%20we%20give%20them%20an%20opportunity%20to%20take%20an%20assessment%20and%20have%20that%20be%20the%20starting%20point%20of%20what%20they%20think%20their%20type%20might%20be.%20We%20walk%20through%20some%20high-level%20understanding%20of%20what%20the%20tool%20is%2C%20how%20it%20works%2C%20and%20how%20you%20can%20use%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20think%20it%20serves%20my%20clients%20to%20come%20in%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20theory%20and%20conceptual%20content.%20So%2C%20after%20that%2C%20we%20practice.%20In%20the%20context%20of%20a%20workshop%2C%20the%20practice%20may%20be%20breaking%20off%20into%20little%20groups.%20We%20create%20a%20scenario%20and%20have%20them%20come%20up%20with%20a%20practical%20way%20they%20can%20apply%20this%20in%20the%20office%20the%20next%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20the%20Enneagram%20focuses%20on%20core%20motivations.%20So%2C%20after%20discussing%20core%20motivations%2C%20I%20say%20to%20a%20team%3A%20%26quot%3BAs%20you're%20about%20to%20engage%20in%20a%20problem-solving%20or%20conflict-oriented%20conversation%2C%20I%20want%20you%20to%20consider%20the%20person%20you%20are%20talking%20to.%20If%20you%20know%20their%20Enneagram%20type%2C%20think%20about%20the%20core%20motivation%20of%20that%20type%20and%20have%20that%20frame%20how%20you're%20going%20to%20approach%20that%20conversation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20come%20back%20the%20next%20month%20for%20our%20coaching%20meeting%2C%20I%20ask%20them%20for%20a%20story%20of%20how%20that%20changed%20the%20trajectory%20of%20the%20conversation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20thing%20I%20love%20most%20is%20when%20I%20have%20a%20story%20told%20through%20tears.%20It's%20amazing%20how%20often%20that%20has%20happened.%20People%20will%20come%20back%20and%20say%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20so%20afraid%20to%20talk%20to%20so-and-so%20about%20this%20topic.%20Then%20I%20realized%20where%20they%20were%20coming%20from%20wasn't%20anger%20and%20animosity%20toward%20me.%20They%20were%20coming%20from%20a%20place%20of%20fear.%20I%20was%20able%20to%20ask%20them%20what%20are%20you%20afraid%20of%3F%20And%20it%20broke%20the%20ice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20tell%20these%20conversations%20in%20tears.%20I%20didn't%20realize%20I%20could%20connect%20with%20people%20at%20that%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20see%20some%20patterns%20in%20my%20Enneagram%20work%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETypes%20threes%2C%20sevens%2C%20and%20eights%20tend%20to%20be%20your%20leaders.%20They%20lead%20in%20different%20styles%20and%20for%20different%20types%20of%20reasons%2C%20but%20they%20tend%20to%20be%20your%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20trend%20I%20see%20is%20that%20out%20of%20the%20nine%20types%2C%20the%20most%20infrequent%20type%20you'll%20see%20in%20a%20leadership%20position%20will%20be%20a%20four.%20Type%20fours%20tend%20to%20be%20very%20internal%20in%20terms%20of%20their%20thinking%20and%20processing.%20They're%20very%20comfortable%20being%20on%20the%20fringes%20and%20on%20the%20outside%20looking%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20see%20that%20types%20one%2C%20five%2C%20and%20six%20tend%20to%20be%20very%20driven%20toward%20process.%20They%20stick%20to%20the%20script.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224833%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20diagram%20of%20the%20nine%20Enneagram%20types%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6539bec496f7540cd06620f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223522%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Enneagram%20is%20a%20personality%20model%20that%20categorizes%20people%20into%20one%20of%20nine%20interconnected%20archetypes%20that%20are%20represented%20by%20numbers%20that%20attempt%20to%20explain%20people's%20characters%20through%20their%20core%20motivations%2C%20desires%2C%20and%20fears.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEvery%20once%20in%20a%20while%20you%20have%20a%20skeptical%20executive%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20don't%20really%20try%20to%20combat%20anybody%20who%20doesn't%20want%20to%20bring%20the%20Enneagram%20in.%20When%20I%20start%20describing%20the%20Enneagram%2C%20it%20just%20somehow%20lands%20because%20it's%20not%20typical%20corporate%20speak.%20It's%20different.%20And%20people%20seem%20to%20want%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20finding%20more%20and%20more%20that%20there%20is%20a%20very%20low%20tolerance%20for%20anything%20that's%20not%20authentic.%20The%20Enneagram%20requires%20each%20of%20us%20to%20look%20inside%20to%20deal%20with%20things%20like%20core%20motivations%2C%20childhood%20messages%2C%20things%20we%20want%20to%20hear%2C%20and%20core%20longings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20reward%20I%20get%20is%20when%20these%20conversations%20move%20from%20their%20workplace%20into%20their%20personal%20lives.%20I'm%20amazed%20at%20how%20many%20people%20come%20back%20and%20say%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20use%20this%20at%20the%20office%2C%20but%20I%20did%20use%20it%20at%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20to%20see%20that%20there%20is%20a%20significant%20change%20and%20transition%20in%20how%20they're%20interacting%20with%20family%20and%20those%20closest%20to%20them.%20If%20they%20can%20change%20their%20lives%20and%20change%20things%20at%20home%2C%20that's%20going%20to%20make%20them%20a%20better%20employee%20and%20a%20better%20staff%20member%20and%20a%20better%20team%20member.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeminars%20are%20great%2C%20books%20are%20great%2C%20conferences%20are%20great.%20But%20there's%20something%20about%20learning%20about%20myself%20together%20in%20a%20community%20that%20brings%20people%20together.%20And%20the%20Enneagram%20is%20a%20great%2C%20great%20tool%20to%20do%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbusiness-coach-uses-enneagram-corporate-trainings-workshop-personality-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698351698000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6539bcb396f7540cd0662080%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbusiness-coach-uses-enneagram-corporate-trainings-workshop-personality-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jay%20Hidalgo%20is%20a%20leadership%20coach%20who%20uses%20the%20Enneagram%20model%20in%20corporate%20workshops.%20He%20told%20Insider%20the%20tool%20is%20great%20for%20building%20team%20cohesion.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22esnodgrass%40insider.com%20(Erin%20Snodgrass)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%2