nt%2F2390086231016000000000001%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiled%20an%20objection%20%3C%2Fa%3Elast%20week%20raising%20Jones'%20conflict%20of%20interest%2C%20among%20other%20issues.%20%26quot%3BYesCare's%20lawyer%20and%20the%20mediator%20who%20presided%20over%20the%20negotiation%20of%20the%20global%20settlement%20in%20this%20case%20share%20a%20household%20and%20are%20involved%20in%20an%20intimate%20relationship%2C%26quot%3B%20Cross%20writes%20in%20the%20objection.%20%26quot%3BHad%20they%20been%20so%20informed%2C%20many%20creditors%20likely%20would%20have%20objected%20to%20the%20appointment%20of%20Judge%20Jones%20as%20mediator.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20goes%20on%20to%20say%20that%20the%20relationship%20%26quot%3Braises%20reasonable%20doubts%20as%20to%20the%20fairness%20of%20the%20mediation%20process.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20from%20nine%20US%20senators%2C%20including%20Elizabeth%20Warren%2C%20Bernie%20Sanders%2C%20Cory%20Booker%2C%20and%20the%20Judiciary%20Committee's%20chair%2C%20Dick%20Durbin%2C%20raises%20the%20issue%20as%20well.%20%26quot%3BCorizon's%20tactics%20are%20further%20called%20into%20question%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20write%2C%20%26quot%3Bgiven%20the%20secret%20romantic%20relationship%20between%20the%20judge%20mediating%20the%20plan%20negotiations%20and%20the%20attorney%20representing%20YesCare%20in%20the%20negotiations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20ruling%20by%20Lopez%20on%20objections%20from%20creditors%20could%20come%20as%20soon%20as%20early%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Extremely%20low%20payouts%20for%20prisoners%20and%20their%20families.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bankruptcy%20plan%20breaks%20creditors%20down%20into%20several%20classes.%20The%20largest%20is%20the%20medical-malpractice%20claimants%2C%20who%20collectively%20say%20they're%20owed%20almost%20%241.1%20billion.%20Claims%20by%20a%20class%20composed%20of%20vendors%20such%20as%20hospitals%20amount%20to%20far%20less%20%E2%80%94%20about%20