ot%3Bserious%20sanctions%26quot%3B%20if%20it's%20violated%2C%20he%20reminds%20his%20readers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20gag%2C%20Trump's%20original%20offending%20Truth%20Social%20post%20remained%20up%20on%20Trump's%20campaign%20website%20for%2017%20days%2C%20Engoron%20notes.%20This%20resulted%20in%20%26quot%3Ba%20%245%2C000%20nominal%20sanction%20against%20Donald%20Trump%20for%20the%20first-time%20violation%20of%20the%20gag%20order.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20countered%20through%20his%20defense%20team%20that%20this%20original%20offending%20post%20%E2%80%94%20falsely%20calling%20Engoron's%20principal%20law%20clerk%2C%20Allison%20Greenfield%20%26quot%3BSchumer's%20girlfriend%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20was%20accidentally%20automatically%20uploaded%20to%20his%20campaign%20website%20by%20underlings%20and%20algorithms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThen%20came%20this%20week's%20violation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221088%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20third%20paragraph%20of%20Justice%20Arthur%20Engoron's%20order%20fining%20Donald%20Trump%20%2410%2C000.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653aa01996f7540cd066c73a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22170%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20third%20paragraph%20of%20Justice%20Arthur%20Engoron's%20order%20fining%20Donald%20Trump%20%2410%2C000.%3Cp%3ENY%20Courts%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20October%2025%2C%20during%20a%20break%20from%20the%20trial%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20made%20the%20following%20statement%20to%20a%20gaggle%20of%20reporters%20outside%20the%20courtroom%3A%20'This%20judge%20is%20a%20very%20partisan%20judge%20with%20a%20person%20who's%20very%20partisan%20sitting%20alongside%20him%2C%20perhaps%20even%20more%20partisan%20than%20he%20is%2C'%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20writes%20now%20of%20what%20happened%20in%20a%20courthouse%20hallway%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BQuite%20clearly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20writes%2C%20%26q