onds.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecession-outlook-us-economy-rising-risks-3-warning-signs-gdp-2023-10%3Futm_medium%3Dnewsletter%26utm_source%3DSailthru%26utm_campaign%3DInsider_Today%5C%22%3Erecession%20everyone's%20been%20waiting%20for%20over%20the%20past%2018%20months%3C%2Fa%3E%20isn't%20coming%20anytime%20soon%20after%20the%20release%20of%20third-quarter%20GDP%20data%2C%20according%20to%20JPMorgan%20portfolio%20manager%20Phil%20Camporeale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20economy%20posted%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgdp-recession-outlook-economy-gross-domestic-product-third-quarter-2023-10%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520US%2520economy%2520is%2520growing%2520at%2520the%2520fastest%2520pace%2520in%25202%2520years%26amp%3Btext%3DReal%2520GDP%2520rose%25204.9%2525%2520at%2Cbe%2520too%2520long%2520or%2520severe.%5C%22%3Ethird-quarter%20GDP%20growth%20of%204.9%25%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20representing%20its%20strongest%20quarterly%20growth%20since%20late%202021%2C%20and%20that's%20after%20multiple%20quarters%20of%20above-trend%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20pace%2C%20the%20economy%20isn't%20signaling%20a%20moderation%20to%20a%20soft%20landing%2C%20he%20said%2C%20suggesting%20no%20slowdown%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20economy%20is%20defying%20gravity%20right%20now%2C%20and%20it's%20the%20gravity%20of%20this%20interest%20rate%20cycle%20that%20nobody%20saw%20coming%2C%26quot%3B%20Camporeale%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2Fvideo%2F2023%2F10%2F26%2Fwe-really-like-us-high-yield-right-now-says-jpmorgans-phil-camporeale.html%3F%26qsearchterm%3DCamporeale%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20CNBC%20on%20Thursday%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20recession%20potentially%20averted%2C%20as%20he%20expects%2C%20investors%20should%20be%20buying%20high-yield%20bonds%20that%20are%20returning%20upwards%20of%209%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20really%20like%20US%20high%20yield%20%5Bbonds%5D.%20US%20high%20yield%20is%20a%20no-recession%20trade.%20A%20soft%20landing%20is%20no%20recession.%20It's%20also%20higher%20for%20longer%2C%20and%20a%20high-yield%20instrument%20yielding%209%25%20is%20really%20attractive%2C%26quot%3B%20Camporeale%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20gauge%20whether%20the%20economy%20is%20going%20to%20enter%20a%20recession%20anytime%20soon%2C%20he%20said%20investors%20need%20to%20monitor%20three%20big%20things%3A%20GDP%2C%20the%20jobs%20market%2C%20and%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20right%20now%2C%20on%20all%20three%20fronts%2C%20it%20doesn't%20look%20like%20a%20recession%20is%20imminent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20GDP%2C%20Camporeale%20highlighted%20that%20near-5%25%20growth%20is%20exceptionally%20strong%2C%20and%20that%20most%20importantly%2C%20it's%20the%20labor%20market%20that%20has%20been%20standing%20tall%20amid%20the%20scary%20headlines%20of%20an%20imminent%20recession.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20labor%20market%20%5Bis%5D%20the%20canary%20in%20the%20coal%20mine.%20That's%20what%20matters%20the%20most%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20labor%20market%20has%20been%20rock%20solid%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20with%20an%20average%20of%20266%2C000%20jobs%20being%20added%20to%20the%20economy%20each%20month%20over%20the%20past%20three%20months.%20Additionally%2C%20there%20are%201.5%20job%20openings%20for%20every%20unemployed%20person%20looking%20for%20work%2C%20and%20weekly%20initial%20jobless%20claims%20continue%20to%20hover%20around%20200%2C000%2C%20which%20is%20exceptionally%20low.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finflation-economy-recession-crash-jobs-market-unemployment-federal-reserve-richsession-2023-7%5C%22%3Erecent%20inflation%20readings%20show%20continued%20progress%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20reaching%20its%20goal%20of%20about%202%25.%3C%2Fp%3