2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fec-says-priyanka-gandhi-himanta-sarmas-speeches-in-violation-of-code-of-conduct-issues-show-cause-notices%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWhatever%20My%20Boys%20Could%20Do%2C%20Daughter%20Could%20Too%26quot%3B%3A%20Nita%20Ambani%20On%20Succession%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFor%20girls%20to%20learn%20that%20they%20are%20equal%20to%20boys%2C%20they%20have%20to%20see%20that%20at%20their%20homes%2C%20says%20Nita%20Ambani%2C%20wife%20of%20Asia's%20richest%20man%20Mukesh%20Ambani%2C%20on%20how%20they%20never%20differentiated%20among%20their%20three%20children%20who%20in%20the%20succession%20planning%20have%20got%20equal%20share%20of%20the%20Reliance%20empire.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMukesh%20and%20Nita%20Ambani%20have%20three%20children%20--%20twins%20Isha%20and%20Akash%2C%2032%2C%20and%20Anant%2C%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20have%20recently%20been%20inducted%20on%20the%20board%20of%20India's%20most%20valuable%20company%20and%20are%20being%20groomed%20to%20take%20over%20its%20three%20almost%20equal%20verticals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsha%2C%20who%20is%20married%20to%20Anand%20Piramal%2C%20son%20of%20Piramal%20Group's%20Ajay%20and%20Swati%20Piramal%2C%20is%20being%20groomed%20for%20retail%2C%20Akash%20for%20digital%2Ftelecom%20and%20Anant%20for%20new%20energy%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20CNBC%20International%2C%20Nita%20Ambani%20spoke%20about%20her%20family%20life%2C%20including%20the%20relationship%20with%20husband%20Mukesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20learnt%20so%20much%20from%20each%20other.%20Mukesh%2C%20as%20I%20say%2C%20has%20the%20floodlights%20in%20life...%20he%20thinks%20far%20ahead%20of%20his%20times.%20While%20I%20get%20into%20the%20meticulous%20details%2C%20he%20calls%20it%20the%20spotlights%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20she%20always%20tells%20her%20children%20that%20the%20single-most%20important%20decision%20is%20choosing%20the%20right%20life%20partner%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20so%20blessed%20to%20have%20Mukesh%2C%20who's%20my%20best%20friend%20and%20my%20life%20partner.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BAnd%2C%20you%20know%2C%20we've%20enjoyed%20the%20journey%20of%20life%2C%20raising%20our%20children%20and%20our%20grandchildren%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20says%20the%20couple%20still%20loves%20doing%20the%20same%20thing%20that%20they%20used%20to%20when%20they%20were%20young.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20he%20takes%20me%20for%20a%20drive%2C%20we%20love%20listening%20to%20Hindi%20music%2C%20eating%20street%20food%2C%20I%20love%20my%20'bhel'%20on%20the%20road%20and%20he%20loves%20his%20'dosa%20idli'.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20we%20still%20love%20doing%20what%20we%20used%20to%20love%20doing.%20So%20these%20are%20the%20values%20that%20we%20kind%20of%20really%20live%20every%20day%20of%20loving%20our%20family%2C%20respecting%20our%20elders%2C%20being%20honest%2C%20humble%2C%20I%20think%20not%20much%20has%20changed%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20children%2C%20she%20said%20Isha%2C%20who%20too%20is%20a%20mother%20of%20twins%2C%20was%20hands%20on%20for%20the%20launch%20of%20Nita%20Mukesh%20Ambani%20Cultural%20Centre%20(NMACC)%20--%20a%20first-of-its-kind%2C%20multi-disciplinary%20cultural%20space%20in%20the%20sphere%20of%20arts%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20now%20she's%20leading%20our%20retail%20(business)%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20I%20think%20for%20girls%20to%20learn%20that%20they%20are%20equal%2C%20they%20have%20to%20see%20that%20(at)%20their%20homes%20they%20have%20mentors%20who%20know%20that%20they're%20not%20anything%20less%20than%20boys.%20I%20have%20never%20differentiated%20between%20Isha%20and%20Akash%20and%20Anant.%20Whatever%20my%20boys%20could%20do%2C%20my%20daughter%20could%20do%20too.%26quot%3B%20And%20this%20has%20been%20reflected%20in%20the%20succession%20at%20Reliance.%20Though%20Isha%20is%20married%20into%20Parimals%2C%20she%20is%20getting%20an%20equal%20share%20in%20the%20business%20as%20her%20brothers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAkash%2C%20Isha%20and%20Anant%20and%20a%20whole%20lot%20of%20the%20young%20generation%20is%20going%20to%20be%20the%20next%20leadership%20for%20Reliance%20and%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20all%20three%20of%20them%2C%20I%20see%20different%20qualities.%20In%20Anant%2C%20my%20youngest%2C%20I%20see%20a%20compassionate%20young%20man%20who%20believes%20in%20conservation%2C%20in%20making%20the%20world%20a%20better%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAkash%20is%20leading%20the%20digital%20revolution%20through%20Jio.%20Isha%20is%20leading%20retail%20besides%20taking%20active%20interest%20in%20Reliance%20Foundation.%20All%20three%20of%20them%20are%20very%2C%20very%20committed%20to%20working%20in%20Reliance.%20They%20have%20their%20own%20strengths%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20tells%20her%20children%20to%20concentrate%20on%20their%20strengths%20and%20make%20them%20stronger.%20%26quot%3BNobody's%20born%20perfect%20or%20nobody%20can%20be%20perfect.%20And%20it%20is%20okay%20to%20make%20mistakes.%20You%20learn%20much%20more%20from%20your%20mistakes%20than%20you%20do%20from%20your%20successes.%20Be%20humble%2C%20Be%20compassionate.%20Treat%20people%20with%20respect.%20And%20I'm%20very%20happy%20for%20the%20new%20young%20generation%20that%20is%20growing%20at%20Reliance%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20Bharatnatyam%20dancer%2C%20Nita%20said%20the%20inspiration%20to%20set%20up%20NMACC%20came%20when%20she%20visited%20Australia%20for%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20and%20saw%20the%20Sydney%20Opera%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20that%20time%2C%20I%20thought%2C%20why%20can't%20India%20have%20something%20like%20this%20of%20its%20own%3F%20So%20the%20idea%20really%20sparked%20off%20at%20that%20time%20in%20Australia.%20And%20it's%20taken%20us%20now%20a%20decade%20to%20bring%20this%20to%20life.%26quot%3B%20Nita%2C%20who%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20International%20Olympics%20Committee%2C%20said%20India%20is%20absolutely%20ready%20to%20host%20the%20Olympics.%20%26quot%3BJust%20like%20we%20would%20love%20to%20have%20the%20Olympics%20in%20India%2C%20the%20Olympics%20also%20cannot%20ignore%20the%201.4%20billion%20people%20of%20India.%26quot%3B%20She%20also%20heads%20Reliance%20Foundation%2C%20the%20philanthropic%20arm%20of%20Reliance%20Industries%20Ltd.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698341820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fq9hclju_nita-ambani-isha-ambani_625x300_26_October_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhatever-my-boys-could-do-daughter-could-too-nita-ambani-on-reliance-succession-plan-4517579%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20girls%20to%20learn%20that%20they%20are%20equal%20to%20boys%2C%20they%20have%20to%20see%20that%20at%20their%20homes%2C%20says%20Nita%20Ambani%2C%20wife%20of%20Asia's%20richest%20man%20Mukesh%20Ambani%2C%20on%20how%20they%20never%20differentiated%20among%20their%20three%20children.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhatever-my-boys-could-do-daughter-could-too-nita-ambani-on-reliance-succession-plan-4517579%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhatever-my-boys-could-do-daughter-could-too-nita-ambani-on-reliance-succession-plan-4517579%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhatever-my-boys-could-do-daughter-could-too-nita-ambani-on-reliance-succession-plan-4517579%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title