been%20made%20to%20portray%20this%20communal%20conflict%20in%20reductionist%20terms%2C%20projected%20to%20the%20world%20as%20the%20Hindu%20majority%20prosecuting%20the%20Christian%20minorities.%20This%20oversimplification%20not%20only%20ignores%20the%20complex%20social%20fabric%20of%20Manipur%2C%20but%20also%20heightens%20tensions%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Rajshree%20said%20in%20the%20Congressional%20hearing%2C%20adding%20the%20attempts%20to%20project%20the%20Manipur%20ethnic%20violence%20as%20a%20religious%20one%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bclassic%20case%20of%20Hinduphobia%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20majority-minority%20debate%20should%20be%20examined%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20intersectionality%20of%20time%2C%20space%2C%20and%20context.%20For%20example%2C%20Christians%20are%20a%20minority%20in%20India%2C%20but%20they%20are%20a%20majority%20in%20the%20northeastern%20region%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Indian-American%20scholar%2C%20who%20holds%20a%20PhD%20in%20Sociology%20specialising%20in%20Gender%20Studies%20and%20Socio%20Anthropology.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20180%20people%20have%20died%20and%20thousands%20internally%20displaced%20after%20ethnic%20clashes%20broke%20out%20in%20Manipur%20on%20May%203%20following%20a%20protest%20by%20the%20Kuki%20tribes%20over%20the%20Meiteis'%20demand%20to%20be%20included%20under%20the%20affirmative%20action%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(ST)%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Rajshree%20said%20Manipur's%20diversity%20is%20its%20strength%2C%20as%20within%20the%20Hindu%20community%20in%20the%20state%2C%20there%20are%20other%20ethnicities%20including%20people%20from%20Punjab%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Nepal%20and%20more.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20Christian%20community%20includes%20Nagas%2C%20Kuki%20and%20also%20Meiteis.%20%26quot%3BThis%20diversity%20is%20not%20a%20source%20of%20division%2C%20but%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20harmonious%20coexistence%20that%20has%20characterised%20Manipur%20for%20generations%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20pointed%20out%20some%20social%20activists%20and%20religious%20leaders%20of%20the%20Christian%20community%20have%20strongly%20denied%20the%20Manipur%20violence%20was%20based%20on%20religious%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMizoram%20activist%20Alinery%20Lian-Luwang%20told%20the%20UN%20that%20'the%20narratives%20peddled%20by%20international%20media%20that%20the%20Manipur%20conflict%20is%20of%20religious%20nature%2C%20holds%20no%20ground'%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Rajshree%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20speech%20by%20the%20activist%20at%20a%20general%20debate%20at%20the%2054th%20session%20of%20the%20UN%20Human%20Rights%20Council%20in%20Geneva.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20The%20Archbishop%20of%20Mumbai%20categorically%20mentioned%2C%20and%20I%20quote%2C%20'It%20is%20given%20a%20religious%20twist%2C%20but%20it%20is%20not%20a%20religious%20conflict%20between%20two%20religions%2C%20it's%20between%20two%20tribes%2C%20and%20we%20must%20now%20not%20do%20anything%20that%20will%20worsen%20the%20situation'%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Rajshree%20said%20at%20the%20Congressional%20hearing%20organised%20by%20HinduACTion%2C%20and%20Namaste%20Shalom%20Multi-Faith%20Alliance%20to%20address%20rising%20antisemitism%20and%20Hinduphobia%20in%20both%20the%20US%20and%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20recent%20times%2C%20there%20has%20been%20an%20alarming%20surge%20in%20attempts%20to%20exploit%20the%20Manipur%20conflict%20as%20a%20platform%20for%20propagating%20Hindu%20hate.%20This%20disturbing%20trend%20has%20found%20traction%20among%20certain%20factions...%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20who%20have%20strategically%20exploited%20religious%20sentiments%20to%20further%20their%20divisive%20agenda.%20What%20is%20even%20more%20concerning%20is%20the%20convergence%20of%20some%20radical%20Islamist%20groups%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20who%20have%20appropriated%20and%20aligned%20themselves%20with%20this%20cause.%20They%20perceive%20this%20situation%20as%20a%20prime%20opportunity%20to%20tarnish%20the%20image%20of%20Hindus%20on%20a%20global%20scale%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Rajshree%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20three%20months%20after%20the%20Manipur%20violence%20began%2C%20a%20speech%20by%20the%20leader%20of%20a%20Canada-based%20Kuki-Zo%20tribes%20group%20from%20Manipur%20over%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20back%20home%20had%20sparked%20a%20massive%20controversy.%20The%20event%20was%20held%20at%20the%20same%20gurdwara%20in%20Canada's%20Surrey%2C%20whose%20chief%20and%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20was%20shot%20dead%20by%20unidentified%20people%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELien%20Gangte%2C%20the%20Canada%20chapter%20chief%20of%20the%20North%20American%20Manipur%20Tribal%20Association%20(NAMTA)%2C%20in%20his%20address%20condemned%20what%20he%20called%20%26quot%3Battacks%20on%20minorities%20in%20India%26quot%3B%20and%20asked%20Canada%20for%20%26quot%3Ball%20possible%20help%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENAMTA%20had%20posted%20a%20video%20of%20the%20event%20on%20Facebook%20and%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20on%20August%207.%20It%20deleted%20the%20videos%20much%20later%20when%20the%20row%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%20surfaced%20following%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau's%20claim%20that%20%26quot%3BIndian%20government%20agents%26quot%3B%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Nijjar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia's%20anti-terror%20body%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%20on%20September%2030%20said%20it%20is%20investigating%20a%20transnational%20conspiracy%20case%20involving%20terrorist%20leaders%20in%20Bangladesh%20and%20Myanmar.%20The%20NIA%20statement%20came%20after%20a%20terror%20accused%2C%20Seiminlun%20Gangte%2C%20was%20arrested%20and%20charged%20with%20conspiring%20with%20Myanmar-%20and%20Bangladesh-based%20leadership%20of%20terror%20outfits%20to%20wage%20war%20against%20India%20by%20exploiting%20the%20ethnic%20unrest%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698340620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F0on6jv0o_rajshree-keisham_625x300_26_October_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhinduphobia-indian-american-scholar-rajshree-keisham-slams-attempts-to-show-manipur-crisis-as-religious-conflict-4517535%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Manipur%20crisis%20is%20a%20complex%20web%20of%20internecine%20conflict%20marked%20by%20violence%2C%20mistrust%2C%20socio-political%20tensions%20and%20a%20deadly%20trifecta%20of%20insurgency%2C%20narcotics%20and%20illegal%20infiltration%2C%20which%20pose%20significant%20threats%20to%20India's%20national%20security.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A23%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhinduphobia-indian-american-scholar-rajshree-keisham-slams-attempts-to-show-manipur-crisis-as-religious-conflict-4517535%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhinduphobia-indian-american-scholar-rajshree-keisham-slams-attempts-to-show-manipur-crisis-as-religious-conflict-4517535%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhinduphobia-indian-american-scholar-rajshree-keisham-slams-attempts-to-show-manipur-crisis-as-religious-conflict-4517535%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20a%201st%2C%20artificial%20intelligence%20company%20from%20Silicon%20Valley%20enters%20Bihar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698340525000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2022-03%2F20%2Ffull%2F1647798220-9844.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fin-a-1st-artificial-intelligence-company-from-silicon-valley-enters-bihar-123102600201_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20company%20currently%20has%20some%204%2C000%20employees%20in%20India%2C%20but%20they%20are%20mo