the%20sky%20after%20a%20blast%20in%20the%20grainy%20night-vision%20footage%20the%20Israeli%20military%20released%20hours%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20declared%20preparations%20for%20a%20ground%20war%20were%20under%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20operation%20in%20northern%20Gaza%20came%20in%20%26quot%3Bpreparation%20for%20the%20next%20stages%20of%20combat%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20military%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20black-and-white%20video%20showed%20armoured%20vehicles%20moving%20near%20Gaza's%20border%20fence.%20Other%20footage%20appeared%20to%20show%20an%20air%20strike%20and%20buildings%20being%20targeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20raid%20came%20after%20Netanyahu%20delivered%20a%20nationally%20televised%20address%20to%20Israelis%20still%20grieving%20and%20furious%20after%20the%20October%207%20attacks%2C%20telling%20them%20%26quot%3Bwe%20are%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20a%20campaign%20for%20our%20existence%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInternational%20alarm%20has%20increased%20amid%20growing%20shock%20about%20the%20scale%20of%20human%20suffering%20inside%20the%20besieged%20Palestinian%20territory%20where%20Israel%20has%20cut%20off%20most%20water%2C%20food%2C%20fuel%20and%20other%20basic%20supplies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20southern%20Gaza%2C%20a%20grieving%20Umm%20Omar%20al-Khaldi%20told%20AFP%20how%20she%20saw%20her%20neighbours%20being%20killed%20in%20an%20Israeli%20strike%20that%20reduced%20the%20house%20to%20rubble%2C%20with%20many%20feared%20buried%20beneath.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20saw%20them%20getting%20bombarded%20--%20the%20children%20got%20bombarded%20while%20their%20mother%20was%20hugging%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20woman%20said%2C%20desperately%20pleading%20for%20help%20from%20the%20outside%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhere%20are%20the%20Arabs%2C%20where%20is%20humanity%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmnesty%20International%20in%20a%20statement%20called%20for%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%20to%20ensure%20%26quot%3Baccess%20to%20life-saving%20aid%20for%20people%20in%20Gaza%20amidst%20an%20unprecedented%20humanitarian%20catastrophe%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20human%20rights%20group's%20chief%20Agnes%20Callamard%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BSerious%20violations%20of%20international%20humanitarian%20law%2C%20including%20war%20crimes%2C%20by%20all%20parties%20to%20the%20conflict%20continue%20unabated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E-%20Surging%20death%20count%20-%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20war's%20surging%20death%20count%20is%20by%20far%20the%20highest%20since%20Israel%20unilaterally%20withdrew%20from%20the%20small%20coastal%20territory%20in%202005%20--%20a%20period%20that%20has%20seen%20four%20previous%20Gaza%20wars.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEntire%20neighbourhoods%20have%20been%20razed%2C%20surgeons%20are%20operating%20without%20anaesthetic%2C%20and%20ice-cream%20trucks%20have%20become%20makeshift%20morgues.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20chaotic%20scenes%2C%20volunteers%20and%20neighbours%20have%20clawed%2C%20sometimes%20with%20their%20bare%20hands%2C%20through%20shattered%20concrete%20and%20sand%20to%20pull%20out%20civilian%20casualties.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20too%20often%20they%20recover%20only%20corpses%20which%20have%20piled%20up%2C%20wrapped%20in%20bloodstained%20white%20shrouds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Brussels%20on%20Thursday%2C%20European%20Union%20leaders%20debated%20calling%20for%20%26quot%3Bpauses%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20war%20so%20aid%20can%20get%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%2027-nation%20bloc%20has%20long%20been%20split%20between%20more%20pro-Palestinian%20members%20such%20as%20Ireland%20and%20Spain%2C%20and%20staunch%20backers%20of%20Israel%20including%20Germany%20and%20Austria.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20want%20is%20the%20killing%20and%20the%20violence%20to%20stop%20so%20that%20humanitarian%20aid%20can%20get%20into%20Gaza%2C%20where%20innocent%20Palestinian%20people%20are%20suffering%2C%20and%20also%20to%20allow%20us%20to%20get%20EU%20citizens%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Irish%20Prime%20Minister%20Leo%20Varadkar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20a%20strong%20supporter%20of%20Israel%2C%20earlier%20joined%20the%20calls%20for%20it%20to%20%26quot%3Bprotect%20innocent%20civilians%26quot%3B%20and%20to%20follow%20the%20%26quot%3Blaws%20of%20war%26quot%3B%20as%20it%20pursues%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFrench%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20warned%20Wednesday%20that%20%26quot%3Ba%20massive%20intervention%20that%20would%20put%20civilian%20lives%20at%20risk%20would%20be%20an%20error%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20Jordan's%20King%20Abdullah%20II%20said%20anger%20at%20the%20suffering%20could%20%26quot%3Blead%20to%20an%20explosion%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E-%20'Raining%20down%20hellfire'%20-%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20--%20amid%20the%20growing%20calls%20to%20temper%20the%20ferocious%20bombing%20campaign%20--%20said%20Israel%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Braining%20down%20hellfire%20on%20Hamas%26quot%3B%20and%20killing%20%26quot%3Bthousands%20of%20terrorists%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20his%20war%20cabinet%20and%20the%20military%20would%20determine%20the%20timing%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bground%20offensive%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20goal%20to%20%26quot%3Beliminate%20Hamas%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bbring%20our%20captives%20home%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20stressed%20that%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20not%20detail%20when%2C%20how%20or%20how%20many%26quot%3B%20forces%20would%20take%20part.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20also%20acknowledged%20for%20the%20first%20time%20that%20he%20would%20have%20to%20explain%20the%20security%20lapses%20exposed%20on%20October%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fault%20will%20be%20examined%20and%20everyone%20will%20have%20to%20give%20answers%2C%20including%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20all%20this%20will%20happen%20later.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBiden%20stressed%20that%20%26quot%3Bwhen%20this%20cris