ted%20Sri%20Lanka'%3A%20Theekshana%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698339335000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104735435%2Cimgsize-53630.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-world-cup%2Fnews%2Fworld-cup-england-underestimated-sri-lanka-maheesh-theekshana-takes-a-jibe-at-defending-champions%2Farticleshow%2F104735324.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sri%20Lankan%20spinner%20Maheesh%20Theekshana%20didn't%20mince%20words%20and%20said%20that%20the%20defending%20champions%20England%20had%20underestimated%20the%20Islanders%20at%20their%20own%20risk.%20Sri%20Lanka%20cruised%20to%20an%20eight-wicket%20defeat%20against%20the%202019%20champions%20England%20and%20dented%20their%20hopes%20of%20reaching%20the%20semifinals%20of%20the%20mega%20tournament.%20The%20Sri%20Lankan%20bowlers%20demonstrated%20remarkable%20accuracy%20on%20a%20pitch%20with%20unpredictable%20bounce%2C%20dismantling%20England's%20lineup%20for%20a%20mere%20156%20runs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-world-cup%2Fnews%2Fworld-cup-england-underestimated-sri-lanka-maheesh-theekshana-takes-a-jibe-at-defending-champions%2Farticleshow%2F104735324.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Centre's%20Plan%20To%20Use%20Officers%20As%20%26quot%3BRath%20Prabharis%26quot%3B%20Hits%20Poll%20Body%20Hurdle%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20government's%20plan%20to%20rope%20in%20bureaucrats%20for%20a%20countrywide%20mega%20rally%20to%20highlight%20its%20achievements%20has%20hit%20a%20roadblock%2C%20with%20the%20Election%20Commission%20banning%20the%20yatra%20in%20five%20states%20where%20elections%20are%20due%20by%20the%20year-end.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20government%20had%20asked%20all%20Union%20ministries%20to%20name%20senior%20officials%20--%20joint%20secretaries%2C%20director%20and%20deputy%20secretary%20--%20from%20every%20district%20of%20the%20country%20to%20act%20as%20%26quot%3Bdistrict%20rath%20prabharis%20(special%20officers)%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20Vikasit%20Bharat%20Sankalp%20Yatra.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20had%20triggered%20protest%20and%20indignation%20among%20a%20section%20of%20officials.%20Former%20bureaucrats%20have%20written%20to%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%2C%20objecting%20to%20the%20plan.%20Rules%20bar%20roping%20in%20civil%20servants%20for%20political%20activities%20so%20as%20to%20enable%20them%20to%20work%20seamlessly%20through%20change%20in%20governments%20at%20the%20Centre%20and%20states.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20pointed%20out%20today%20that%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20has%20already%20come%20into%20effect%20in%20five%20states%20where%20elections%20are%20due%20--%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Mizoram%20and%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20view%20of%20the%20foregoing%2C%20Commission%20has%20directed%20that%20the%20aforesaid%20activities%20should%20not%20be%20taken%20in%20the%20constituencies%20where%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20is%20in%20force%20up%20till%205th%20December%2C%202023%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Commission%20said%20in%20its%20communication%20to%20the%20cabinet%20secretary.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Commission's%20directive%20came%20following%20a%20complaint%20from%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20who%20also%20wrote%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Sunday%2C%20calling%20the%20move%20a%20%26quot%3Bgross%20misuse%20of%20government%20machinery%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20clear%20violation%20of%20the%20Central%20Civil%20Services%20(Conduct)%20Rules%2C%201964%2C%20which%20directs%20that%20no%20government%20servant%20shall%20take%20part%20in%20any%20political%20activity%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kharge%20wrote.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20it%20is%20acceptable%20for%20government%20officers%20to%20disseminate%20information%2C%20to%20make%20them%20celebrate%20and%20showcase%20achievements%20blatantly%20turns%20them%20into%20political%20workers%20of%20the%20ruling%20party.%20The%20fact%20that%20only%20achievements%20of%20the%20last%209%20years%20are%20being%20considered%2C%20gives%20away%20the%20fact%20that%20this%20is%20a%20transparently%20political%20order%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20five-state%20elections%20and%20the%20general%20elections%20of%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20the%20letter%2C%20which%20Mr%20Kharge%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20government%2C%20though%2C%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20yatra%20will%20skip%20poll-bound%20states.%20In%20an%20informal%20interaction%20with%20reporters%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting%20Secretary%20Apurva%20Chandra%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20plan%20to%20start%20the%20'Viksit%20Bharat%20Sankalp%20Yatra'%20in%20election-bound%20states%20where%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20is%20in%20place.%20In%20poll-bound%20states%20the%20yatra%20will%20start%20when%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20is%20lifted%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698339180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2Fkh7g0i2_bjp-generic-1200_625x300_08_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstop-the-yatra-with-senior-officials-as-rath-prabharis-in-poll-bound-areas-election-commission-writes-to-centre-4517242%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government's%20plan%20to%20rope%20in%20bureaucrats%20for%20a%20countrywide%20mega%20rally%20to%20highlight%20its%20achievements%20has%20hit%20a%20roadblock%2C%20with%20the%20Election%20Commission%20banning%20the%20yatra%20in%20five%20states%20where%20elections%20are%20due%20by%20the%20year-end.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstop-the-yatra-with-senior-officials-as-rath-prabharis-in-poll-bound-areas-election-commission-writes-to-centre-4517242%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstop-the-yatra-with-senior-officials-as-rath-prabharis-in-poll-bound-areas-election-commission-writes-to-centre-4517242%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstop-the-yatra-with-senior-officials-as-rath-prabharis-in-poll-bound-areas-election-commission-writes-to-centre-4517242%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%228%20Navy%20Veterans%20Get%20Death%20In%20Qatar%2C%20%26quot%3BShocked%26quot%3B%20India%20To%20Contest%20Order%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEight%20former%20Indian%20Navy%20personnel%20have%20been%20handed%20death%20penalty%20in%20Qatar.%20Calling%20the%20judgement%20%26quot%3Bshocking%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20foreign%20ministry%20said%20it%20would%20not%20comment%20given%20the%20%26quot%3Bconfidential%20nature%20of%20proceedings%26quot%3B%20but%20assured%20that%20it%20would%20contest%20the%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20men%2C%20including%20decorated%20officers%20who%20once%20commanded%20major%20Indian%20warships%2C%20were%20working%20for%20Dahra%20Global%20Technologies%20and%20Consultancy%20Services%2C%20a%20private%20firm%20that%20provided%20training%20and%20related%20services%20to%20Qatar's%20armed%20forces.%20Sources%20said%20some%20of%20them%20were%20working%20on%20a%20highly%20sensitive%20project%20--%20Italian%20technology-based%20midget%20submarines%20with%20stealth%20characteristics.%20Reports%20claim%20they%20have%20been%20accused%20of%20spying.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20men%20have%20been%20in%20jail%20since%20August%202022.%20Granted%20consular%20access%20to%20them%2C%20New%20Delhi%20has%20been%20working%20to%20secure%20their%20release.%20The%20men%20went%20to%20trial%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETheir%20bail%20pleas%20were%20rejected%20nu