n%20as%20Operation%20Eagle%20Claw%2C%20ended%20in%20disaster%20after%20encountering%20sandstorms%20and%20mechanical%20problems.%20The%20judiciary's%20Mizan%20Online%20news%20agency%20reported%20that%20during%20the%20operation%2C%20US%20forces%20had%20%26quot%3Battacked%26quot%3B%20a%20bus%20carrying%20Iranian%20passengers.%20This%20comes%20after%20previous%20multi-billion%20dollar%20compensation%20awards%20against%20Tehran%20by%20US%20courts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Firan-court-orders-us-to-pay-damages-for-1980-hostage-rescue-bid%2Farticleshow%2F104735347.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Firan-court-orders-us-to-pay-damages-for-1980-hostage-rescue-bid%2Famp_articleshow%2F104735347.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Firan-court-orders-us-to-pay-damages-for-1980-hostage-rescue-bid%2Famp_articleshow%2F104735347.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sachin%20Pilot%20Defends%20Rajasthan%20Govt%2C%20Says%20ED%20Raids%20as%20BJP%20Thinks%20It%20Is%20Losing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F13181319%2FFtcLijEaYAMzLx6.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Congress%20leader%20and%20former%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20of%20Rajasthan%20Sachin%20Pilot%20has%20said%20that%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%E2%80%99s%20actions%20in%20the%20poll-bound%20state%20on%20Thursday%20(October%2026)%20will%20not%20see%20any%20desertions%20from%20the%20party%20to%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20chief%20minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fgoondagardi-says-ashok-gehlot-as-ed-summons-his-son-raids-rajasthan-congress-chief%5C%22%3EAshok%20Gehlot%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Egoondagardi%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fa%3E(hooliganism)%20after%20the%20ED%20issued%20summons%20to%20his%20son%2C%20Vaibhav%20Gehlot%2C%20and%20conducted%20raids%20on%20state%20Congress%20chief%20Govind%20Singh%20Dotasra.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20son%20has%20been%20summoned%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20recent%20ED%20raids%20against%20Rajasthan-based%20hospitality%20group%20Triton%20Hotels%20%26amp%3B%20Resorts%20Pvt.%20Ltd.%2C%20Vardha%20Enterprises%20Pvt.%20Ltd.%20and%20its%20directors%20and%20promoters%20Shiv%20Shankar%20Sharma%2C%20Rattan%20Kant%20Sharma%2C%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20raids%20on%20Dotasra%20in%20Sikar%20and%20Jaipur%20are%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20money%20laundering%20investigation%20into%20an%20exam%20paper%20leak%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20a%20question%20asked%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Eat%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20about%20whether%20the%20ED%20actions%20have%20raised%20concerns%20about%20leaders%20leaving%20the%20party%20and%20the%20BJP%20being%20in%20touch%20with%20them%2C%20as%20has%20been%20seen%20in%20several%20opposition%20states%20where%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmaharashtra-five-ncp-leaders-who-have-moved-over-to-shinde-govt-are-facing-corruption-cases%5C%22%3Eleaders%20under%20the%20scanner%20of%20central%20agencies%20have%20joined%20the%20BJP%3C%2Fa%3E%20(most%20recently%20in%20Maharashtra)%2C%20Pilot%20said%20that%20the%20ED%E2%80%99s%20actions%20will%20not%20have%20any%20such%20fallout.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20elections%20are%20so%20close%2C%20any%20individual%20who%20wanted%20to%20or%20has%20to%20leave%20the%20political%20party%20may%20have%20already%20done%20so.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20these%20actions%20are%20going%20to%20have%20a%20fallout%20where%20people%20will%20now%20want%20to%20leave%20or%20join%20parties.%20Before%20every%20election%2C%20some%20individuals%20leave%20the%20parties%20and%20some%20join%20other%20parties.%20It%20is%20a%20very%20natural%20thing%20that%20happens%20in%20almost%20every%20state%20in%20every%20election.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20give%20it%20too%20much%20credence%2C%20these%20things%20may%20happen%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20fight%20the%20elections%20based%20on%20our%20performance%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years%20and%20what%20we%20intend%20to%20do%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years.%20I%20am%20yet%20to%20see%20a%20roadmap%20from%20the%20BJP%20for%20the%20next%20five%20years%20%E2%80%93%20this%20is%20our%20blueprint%2C%20this%20is%20the%20work%20that%20we%20will%20do.%20They%20make%20allegations%20but%20don%E2%80%99t%20look%20within%20themselves%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20probe%20their%20own%20leaders%20and%20only%20target%20the%20Congress%20without%20any%20agenda%20or%20roadmap%20for%20the%20state%20of%20Rajasthan.%20How%20will%20people%20believe%20that%3F%20The%20BJP%20has%20lost%20every%20by-election%20in%20these%20last%20five%20years.%20Even%20today%20the%20amount%20of%20chaos%20that%20is%20happening%20within%20the%20BJP%20%E2%80%93%20it%20is%20not%20for%20me%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20internal%20politics%20%E2%80%93%20but%20the%20fact%20of%20the%20matter%20is%20that%20there%20is%20huge%20unrest%20in%20its%20own%20cadre.%20But%20that%20is%20for%20them%20to%20deal%20with.%20I%20am%20just%20saying%20that%20we%20are%20fighting%20this%20election%20unitedly%2C%20we%20are%20fighting%20because%20we%20work%20on%20the%20grassroots.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20whatever%20the%20Congress%20party%20manifesto%20was%2C%20we%20have%20tried%20to%20achieve%20most%20of%20what%20we%20announced%20in%20the%20manifesto.%20We%20have%20announced%20two%20guarantees%20yesterday%20(October%2025)%20and%20will%20announce%20more.%20We%20are%20campaigning%20very%20aggressively%20based%20on%20issues.%20We%20are%20not%20doing%20personalised%20targeting%20using%20unparliamentary%20language%20to%20attack%20our%20opponents.%20We%20are%20fighting%20on%20people%E2%80%99s%20issues%20and%20what%20we%20have%20done%20and%20what%20we%20will%20do.%20I%20am%20very%20confident%20that%20no%20matter%20what%20happens%20the%20Congress%20party%20will%20secure%20a%20very%20substantial%20mandate%20in%20the%20elections.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20while%20addressing%20the%20press%20conference%2C%20Pilot%20said%20that%20the%20ED%20action%2C%20while%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20is%20in%20place%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20shows%20that%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%20is%20attempting%20to%20intimidate%20the%20opposition%20by%20misusing%20central%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20actions%20taken%20by%20the%20agencies%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20in%20Jaipur%20and%20other%20cities%20today%E2%80%A6%20The%20timing%2C%20purpose%2C%20and%20intent%20of%20those%20actions%20are%20completely%20questionable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20action%20has%20come%20as%20the%20BJP%20is%20losing%20the%20upcoming%20elections%20in%20five%20states%20that%20go%20to%20the%20polls%20next%20month%2C%20including%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20they%20were%20winning%20these%20elections%2C%20then%20such%20action%20would%20not%20be%20taking%20place.%20This%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20states%20going%20to%20election%20are%20being%20targeted.%20When%20elections%20end%20these%20cases%20also%20disappear%20from%20headlines.%20This%20does%20not%20bode%20well%20for%20Indian%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20has%20happened%20today%2C%20the%20whole%20state%20has%20seen.%20This%20action%20is%20politically%20motivated.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Thursday%2C%20at%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20Union%20minister%20Gajendra%20Singh%20Shekhawat%20said%20that%20the%20Rajasthan%20government%20has%20%E2%80%9Ccrossed%20all%20milestones%20of%20corruption.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPilot%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20government%20in%20Rajasthan%20is%20against%20corruption.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20the%20ED%20is%20acting%20and%20the%20BJP%20is%20giving%20an%20explanation.%20They%20are%20using%20central%20agencies%20as%20political%20weapons%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698338954000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F13181319%2FFtcLijEaYAMzLx6.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsachin-pilot-defends-rajasthan-state-govt-says-ed-raids-as-bjp-thinks-it-is-losing%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20response%20to%20a%20question%20by%20The%20Wire%2C%20Pilot%20said%20that%20those%20who%20had%20to%20leave%20the%20party%20have%20already%20done%20so%20and%20the%20Congress%20will%20fight%20the%20elections%20next%20month%20%E2%80%98unitedly%E2%80%99.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsachin-pilot-defends-rajasthan-state-govt-says-ed-raids-as-bjp-thinks-it-is-losing%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amitabh's%20Khakee%20to%20get%20a%20sequel%20after%2020%20years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698338850000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104735320%2Cimgsize-47996.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Famitabh-bachchans-khakee-to-get-a-sequel-after-20-years-confirms-late-producers-son-aryeman-ramsay%2Farticleshow%2F104735315.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104735315.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EFilmmaker%20Aryeman%20Ramsay%20is%20planning%20to%20make%20a%20sequel%20to%20the%202004%20film%20'Khakee'%20to%20commem