%20explains%2C%20%26quot%3BYou're%20going%20to%20work%2090%2C000%20hours%20(around%2035%20years)%20over%20your%20lifetime.%20Most%20Americans%20get%20to%20the%20age%20of%2060%20and%20they%20have%20nothing%20to%20show%20for%20it.%20What%20you're%20going%20to%20have%20is%20at%20least%20a%20million%20dollars%20in%20your%20retirement%20account%20if%20you%20pay%20yourself%20first%2C%20one%20hour%20a%20day%20of%20your%20income.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698333420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fq2h5gc28_david-bach_625x300_26_October_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmillionaire-reveals-1-habit-that-will-help-you-become-rich-4517111%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20New%20York%20Times%20bestselling%20author%20and%20self-made%20millionaire%20said%20that%20one%20should%20set%20aside%20at%20least%2014%20per%20cent%20of%20their%20income.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmillionaire-reveals-1-habit-that-will-help-you-become-rich-4517111%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmillionaire-reveals-1-habit-that-will-help-you-become-rich-4517111%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmillionaire-reveals-1-habit-that-will-help-you-become-rich-4517111%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22G-Dragon%20reacts%20to%20support%20from%20fans%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698333380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104734215%2Cimgsize-58846.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Fg-dragon-hits-like-as-international-fans-support-him-amidst-drugs-allegations%2Farticleshow%2F104734217.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%2