ngagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Frasha-thadani-wishes-mom-raveena-tandon-on-her-49th-birthday-with-an-adorable-post-see-inside%2Farticleshow%2F104732325.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Narayana%20Murthy%20Suggests%2070-Hour%20Work%20Week%20To%20Youngsters%2C%20Sparks%20Debate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EInfosys%20founder%20NR%20Narayana%20Murthy%20has%20said%20that%20India's%20work%20culture%20needs%20to%20change%20and%20youngsters%20should%20be%20prepared%20to%20work%20for%2070%20hours%20a%20week%20if%20the%20country%20has%20to%20compete%20effectively%20on%20the%20global%20stage.%20The%2077-year-old%20was%20speaking%20to%20former%20Infosys%20CEO%20Mohandas%20Pai%20on%20the%20first%20episode%20of%203one4%20Capital's%20podcast%20'The%20Record'.%20Mr%20Narayana%20Murthy%20drew%20parallels%20to%20Japan%20and%20Germany%2C%20countries%20that%20implemented%20the%20extended%20working%20hours.%20He%20also%20talked%20about%20other%20topics%20like%20nation%20building%2C%20technology%2C%20his%20company%20Infosys%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20his%20vision%20for%20the%20next%2010%2C%2015%20years%2C%20Mr%20Narayana%20Murthy%20highlighted%20a%20need%20to%20improve%20productivity%20in%20India%20and%20sort%20out%20the%20government%20delays.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia's%20work%20productivity%20is%20one%20of%20the%20lowest%20in%20the%20world.%20Unless%20we%20improve%20our%20work%20productivity%2C%20unless%20we%20reduce%20corruption%20in%20the%20government%20at%20some%20level%2C%20because%20we%20have%20been%20reading%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20the%20truth%20of%20it%2C%20unless%20we%20reduce%20the%20delays%20in%20our%20bureaucracy%20in%20taking%20this%20decision%2C%20we%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20compete%20with%20those%20countries%20that%20have%20made%20tremendous%20progress%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Infosys%20founder%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20therefore%2C%20my%20request%20is%20that%20our%20youngsters%20must%20say%20'this%20is%20my%20country.%20I'd%20like%20to%20work%2070%20hours%20a%20week'%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWatch%20the%20full%20video%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FES8ZNSTswrs%3Fsi%3DldbG5aymHYHK9ThO%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Narayana%20Murthy%20then%20presented%20some%20historical%20examples%20-%20of%20Germany%20and%20Japan%20after%20the%20Second%20World%20War%20-%20to%20underline%20the%20critical%20role%20of%20discipline%20and%20enhanced%20productivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20exactly%20what%20the%20Germans%20and%20Japanese%20did%20after%20the%20Second%20World%20War...%20they%20made%20sure%20that%20every%20German%20worked%20extra%20hours%20for%20a%20certain%20number%20of%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Narayana%20Murthy%20said%20on%20the%20podcast.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20it%20is%20very%20important%20for%20our%20youngsters%20to%20transform%20since%20they%20form%20a%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20majority%20of%20our%20population%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bare%20the%20ones%20who%20can%20build%20our%20country%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20be%20disciplined%20and%20improve%20our%20work%20productivity.%20I%20think%20unless%20we%20do%20that%2C%20what%20can%20poor%20government%20do%3F%20And%20every%20government%20is%20as%20good%20as%20the%20culture%20of%20the%20people.%20And%20our%20culture%20has%20to%20change%20to%20that%20of%20highly%20determined%2C%20extremely%20disciplined%20and%20extremely%20hard-working%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Narayana%20Murthy%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20comments%20sparked%20a%20debate%20among%20users%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAgree%20with%20him...%20work%2040%20hours%20for%20your%20employer%20and%2030%20hours%20for%20your%20own%20interests%2C%26quot%3B%20commented%20one%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCompletely%20disagree%20about%20the%2070%20hours%20a%20week!%20According%20to%20the%2070%20hours%20work%20week%20we%20will%20be%20the%20best%20country%2C%20but%20at%20what%20cost%3F%20What%20will%20that%20individual%20achieve%20after%20working%2070%20hours%20a%20week%3F%20Good%20health%3F%20Good%20family%3F%20Good%20companion%3F%20Happiness%3F%20Fulfillment%3F%20What%20will%20the%20individual%20achieve%3F%20If%20the%20individual%20is%20aiming%20for%20success%20after%20working%2070%20hours%20a%20week%2C%20I%20would%20like%20that%20individual%20to%20define%20success%3F%26quot%3B%20asked%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20companies%20also%20need%20to%20pay%20on%20hourly%20basis...%20Indian%20companies%20won't%20do%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20third%20user%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698328020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2F8gvtrmao_narayana-murthy_625x300_27_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnarayana-murthy-suggests-70-hour-work-week-to-youngsters-sparks-debate-4516739%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Narayana%20Murthy%20presented%20some%20historical%20examples%20-%20of%20Germany%20and%20Japan%20after%20the%20Second%20World%20War%20-%20to%20underline%20the%20critical%20role%20of%20discipline%20and%20enhanced%20productivity.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnarayana-murthy-suggests-70-hour-work-week-to-youngsters-sparks-debate-4516739%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnarayana-murthy-suggests-70-hour-work-week-to-youngsters-sparks-debate-4516739%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%