fices.%20Watch%20the%20video%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20his%20journey.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Pranita%20Bhat%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333028%2Fworld-cup-india-bowler-jasprit-bumrah-inspiring-story-mother-role-model%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%228%20Navy%20Veterans%20Sentenced%20To%20Death%20In%20Qatar%3A%20They%20Commanded%20Warships%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEight%20former%20Indian%20Navy%20officers%2C%20who%20have%20been%20sentenced%20to%20death%20in%20Qatar%2C%20have%20been%20accused%20of%20spying%20for%20Israel.%20The%20eight%20men%20were%20working%20for%20a%20private%20firm%20that%20helped%20the%20Qatari%20armed%20forces%20and%20included%20decorated%20officers%20who%20once%20commanded%20Indian%20warships.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202022%2C%20the%20retired%20officers%20were%20arrested%20on%20charges%20of%20spying%20and%20were%20accused%20of%20espionage%20and%20state-sponsored%20terrorism.%20According%20to%20reports%2C%20the%20eight%20men%20were%20spying%20for%20Qatar%20on%20a%20secret%20naval%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20convicted%20men%20are%20Captain%20Navtej%20Singh%20Gill%2C%20Captain%20Birendra%20Kumar%20Verma%2C%20Captain%20Saurabh%20Vasisht%2C%20Commander%20Amit%20Nagpal%2C%20Commander%20Purnendu%20Tiwari%2C%20Commander%20Sugunakar%20Pakala%2C%20Commander%20Sanjeev%20Gupta%20and%20Sailor%20Ragesh%20Gopakumar.%20They%20worked%20for%20a%20private%20firm%2C%20Dahra%20Global%20Technologies%20and%20Consultancy%20Services%2C%20which%20provided%20training%20and%20other%20services%20for%20Qatar's%20armed%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20said%20it%20was%20shocked%20by%20the%20verdict%20and%20would%20take%20up%20the%20issue%20with%20Qatari%20authorities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAward-Winning%20Commander%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20men%2C%20who%20were%20arrested%20in%20Doha%20last%20year%2C%20have%20been%20accused%20of%20spying%20on%20Qatar's%20advanced%20submarines%20for%20Israel.%20These%20submarines%20were%20coated%20with%20special%20materials%20that%20enhanced%20their%20stealth%20capabilities%2C%20something%20that%20would%20be%20valuable%20for%20any%20navy%20in%20the%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20the%20submarines%20were%20being%20built%20in%20collaboration%20with%20an%20Italian%20shipbuilding%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Commander%20Purnendu%20Tiwari%20was%20awarded%20the%20Pravasi%20Bharatiya%20Samman%2C%20the%20highest%20honour%20conferred%20on%20overseas%20Indians.%20In%20a%20post%20at%20the%20time%2C%20the%20Indian%20Embassy%20in%20Doha%20had%20said%20the%20award%20was%20given%20to%20Commander%20Tiwari%20for%20enhancing%20India's%20image%20abroad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20award%20is%20in%20recognition%20of%20his%20contribution%20towards%20capacity%20building%20for%20the%20Qatar%20Emiri%20Naval%20Forces%2C%20thereby%20promoting%20India-Qatar%20bilateral%20cooperation.%20He%20is%20the%20first%20Indian%20Armed%20Forces%20personnel%20to%20be%20awarded%20this%20highest%20honour%20meant%20for%20NRIs%20%2F%20PIOs%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20embassy%20had%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECommander%20Tiwari%20was%20the%20Managing%20Director%20of%20Dahra%20Global%20Technologies%20and%20Consultancy%20Services%20and%20had%20commanded%20several%20warships%20when%20he%20was%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20Navy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Exploring%20All%20Options'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBail%20petitions%20of%20the%20eight%20men%20had%20been%20rejected%20several%20times%20and%20the%20verdict%20against%20them%20was%20pronounced%20on%20Thursday%20by%20the%20Court%20of%20First%20Instance%20in%20Qatar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20verdict%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20said%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%