20are%20citizens%20of%20Israel%2C%20Palestinians%20who%20live%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20and%20Palestinians%20who%20live%20in%20Gaza%20and%20how%20popular%20it%20is%20in%20Gaza%20today.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAsked%20if%20a%20free%2C%20fair%20and%20credible%20election%20were%20to%20be%20held%20in%20Gaza%20today%2C%20the%20way%20it%20had%20happened%20in%202006%2C%20would%20Hamas%20win%20a%20victory%2C%20Iriqat%20categorically%20said%20no.%20In%20fact%2C%20she%20clearly%20suggested%20that%20a%20free%20and%20fair%20election%20is%20perhaps%20the%20best%20way%20of%20diminishing%20and%20reducing%20Hamas.%20But%20the%20Israelis%2C%20she%20says%2C%20will%20not%20allow%20a%20free%20and%20fair%20election.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20a%20transcript%20of%20Iriqat%E2%80%99s%20interview.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20lightly%20for%20clarity%20and%20style.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKaran%20Thapar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Hello%20and%20welcome%20to%20a%20special%20interview%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%20On%20the%2017th%20day%20of%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%2C%20we%20ask%20what%20it%20is%20like%20to%20be%20a%20Palestinian%20in%20Israel.%20Joining%20me%20now%20from%20Ramallah%20to%20answer%20that%20question%20is%20a%20professor%20at%20the%20Arab%20American%20University%20of%20Palestine%2C%20Dalal%20Iriqat.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Iriqat%2C%20I%20want%20to%20talk%20to%20you%20about%20what%20it%E2%80%99s%20like%20to%20be%20Palestinian%20in%20Israel.%20I%E2%80%99m%20told%20Palestinians%20in%20Israel%20fall%20into%20three%20broad%20categories%3A%20citizens%20of%20Israel%2C%20those%20who%20live%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20where%20Israel%20is%20effectively%20a%20colonising%20power%2C%20and%20those%20who%20live%20in%20Gaza%20blockaded%20and%20besieged%20by%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20start%20with%20Palestinians%2C%20who%20are%20citizens%20of%20Israel.%20I%E2%80%99m%20told%20there%20are%20some%20two%20million%20of%20them.%20Do%20they%20have%20equal%20rights%20with%20Jews%20or%20are%20they%20second-class%20citizens%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Without%20Israel's%20Oppression%20of%20Palestinians%2C%20Hamas%20Terrorism%20Would%20Have%20Never%20Existed%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwithout-israels-oppression-of-palestinians-hamas-terrorism-would-have-never-existed%5C%22%3EWithout%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20Oppression%20of%20Palestinians%2C%20Hamas%20Terrorism%20Would%20Have%20Never%20Existed%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDalal%20Iriqat%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Well%2C%20thank%20you%20very%20much.%20Those%20two%20million%20Palestinians%20who%20live%20in%20Israel%20hold%20Israeli%20citizenship%2C%20but%20it%20was%20documented%20that%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20enjoy%20equal%20rights%20as%20any%20other%20Israeli%20%E2%80%9CJewish%20citizen%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Israel%2C%20they%20had%20passed%20in%20the%20Knesset%2C%20which%20is%20the%20parliament%20of%20the%20Israeli%20people%2C%20what%20is%20called%20the%20Jewish%20Nation%20State%20Law%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Jewish%20Nation%20State%20Law%20stipulated%20very%20bluntly%20that%20those%20who%20enjoy%20full%20rights%20in%20Israel%20are%20the%20Jewish%20citizens%20of%20Israel%20alone%2C%20not%20only%20depriving%20two%20million%20Palestinians%20%E2%80%93%20and%20those%20are%20of%20course%20Muslims%20and%20Christians%20and%20atheists%2C%20if%20you%20want%20%E2%80%93%20of%20the%20basic%20rights%2C%20but%20also%20all%20the%20other%20minorities%20who%20might%20be%20living%20in%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20are%20not%20a%20Jewish%20citizen%20of%20Israel%2C%20you%20are%20a%20second%20or%20third-class%20citizen.%20This%20of%20course%20applies%20to%20the%20Palestinians%20who%20live%20there.%20So%20the%20Palestinians%E2%80%93yeah%2C%20go%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Sorry%2C%20I%20was%20just%20going%20to%20say%2C%20this%20is%20why%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98apartheid%20state%E2%80%99%20is%20used%20for%20Israel.%20Is%20that%20right%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDI%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Yes%2C%20and%20let%E2%80%99s%20be%20clear%20here%2C%20apartheid%20is%20not%20only%20a%20term%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20only%20a%20label%20or%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20an%20invention%20that%20the%20Palestinians%20came%20up%20with.%20Apartheid%2C%20under%20international%20law%2C%20by%20definition%20is%20a%20sort%20of%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20also%20clarify%20to%20your%20audience%20and%20to%20Indians%20in%20general%20that%20it%20was%20international%20human%20rights%20organisations%20which%20conducted%20research%20and%20which%20approved%20and%20documented%20the%20crimes%20of%20apartheid%20against%20the%20Palestinians%20who%20are%20not%20only%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20but%20also%20the%20Palestinians%20who%20live%20inside%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20documented%20crime%2C%20and%20international%20human%20rights%20organisations%20and%20Israeli%20human%20rights%20organisations%20also%20documented%20the%20crime.%20This%20is%20a%20very%20important%20message%20to%20convey%20to%20your%20audiences%20that%20Israel%20is%20committing%20the%20crime%20of%20apartheid%20under%20the%20framework%20of%20the%20Israeli%20military%20prolonged%20occupation%20for%2075%20years%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26163604%2FApartheid-street-1024x768.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26163604%2FApartheid-street-1024x768.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2