ulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20So%20the%20law%20of%20return%20in%20Israel%20directly%20breaches%20the%20resolution%20194%20of%20the%20UN.%20It%20is%20a%20direct%20defiance%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDI%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Yes%2C%20and%20there%20is%20no%20other%20interpretation%20for%20that.%20All%20the%20UN%20and%20the%20international%20community%20understands%20very%20well%20that%20there%20is%20an%20embedded%20right%20for%20the%20Palestinians%20in%20194%20and%20there%20is%20a%20blunt%20violation%20%5Bof%5D%20it%20by%20the%20Israeli%20military%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Now%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20there%20have%20been%20serious%20protests%20in%20Israel%20against%20Prime%20Minister%20Netanyahu%E2%80%99s%20attempts%20to%20dilute%20the%20power%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20I%E2%80%99m%20told%20that%20whenever%20laws%20that%20discriminate%20against%20Palestinians%20are%20challenged%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20upholds%20those%20laws%20and%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20strike%20them%20down.%20So%20are%20Palestinians%20also%20second-class%20citizens%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20judiciary%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25124531%2FIsrael-judicial-reform-protests-II-1024x512.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25124531%2FIsrael-judicial-reform-protests-II-1024x512.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25124531%2FIsrael-judicial-reform-protests-II-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25124531