0They%20are%20protected%20by%20the%20Israeli%20military%20army.%20Military%20soldiers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20also%20want%20to%20clarify%20to%20the%20Indian%20audience%20that%20they%20need%20to%20understand%20that%2030%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20Palestinians%20had%20made%20a%20big%20concession%2C%20because%20we%20believe%20in%20peace%2C%20because%20we%20believe%20in%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20peoples%20of%20Israel%20to%20live%20in%20peace%20and%20security.%20We%20agreed%20to%20the%20two-state%20solution%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9867%20border%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20that%20we%20gave%20up%20on%2078%25%20of%20historic%20Palestine.%20We%20accepted%20%E2%80%93%20as%20the%20PLO%2C%20which%20is%20the%20legitimate%20representative%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20%E2%80%93%20we%20accepted%20to%20have%20our%20own%20state%20on%2022%25%20of%20Mandated%20Palestine.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20two-state%20solution%20was%20the%20position%20of%20the%20international%20community.%20It%20was%20the%20concession%20that%20the%20PLO%20gave%20in%20our%20will%20and%20hopes%20for%20bringing%20peace%2C%20prosperity%20and%20security%20to%20the%20Palestinians%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Israelis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20did%20we%20gain%20after%2030%20years%20of%20procrastinated%20so-called%20peace%20talks%3F%20More%20settlers%2C%20more%20settlements%2C%20no%20possibility%20on%20the%20ground%20of%20any%20independence%20of%20sovereignty%20for%20the%20Palestinian%20people.%20More%20extrajudicial%20killings%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%2C%20more%20detentions%20%E2%80%93%20you%20know%20that%205%2C200%20Palestinians%20are%20still%20%5Bbehind%5D%20Israeli%20bars%2C%20you%20know%2C%20inside%20the%20Israeli%20prisons%2C%20suffering%20from%20every%20kind%20of%20racism%20and%20punishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%201%2C264%20who%20are%20administratively%20detained%2C%20and%20I%20want%20to%2C%20you%20know%2C%20explain%20this%20to%20the%20Indian%20audience%20because%20I%E2%80%99m%20sure%20they