20as%20you%20said%20%E2%80%93%20I%E2%80%99m%20just%2C%20again%2C%20highlighting%20this%20for%20an%20Indian%20audience%20%E2%80%93%20even%20your%20hope%20of%20being%20able%20to%20form%20an%20independent%2C%20sovereign%20Palestine%20state%20on%20just%2022%25%20has%20been%20quashed%20by%20the%20settlers%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20do%20so%20%5Bsic%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20also%20means%20that%20because%20of%20continuing%20Israeli%20control%20on%20what%20is%20accepted%20internationally%20as%20your%20land%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20even%20there%20second-class%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%20I%20notice%2C%20since%20October%207th%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20quoting%20%3Cem%3EAl%20Jazeera%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9Cover%2091%20Palestinian%20people%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20clashes%20with%20settlers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20since%20the%207th%20of%20October.%20Are%20these%20clashes%20a%20recent%20development%20or%20have%20they%20been%20happening%20regularly%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDI%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Israelis%20tried%20to%20mislead%20audiences%20that%20this%20whole%20thing%20started%20on%20the%207th%20of%20October.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20truly%20explain%20the%20reality%20and%20convey%20the%20reality%20and%20the%20right%20narration%2C%20because%20people%20in%20India%20deserve%20to%20learn%20the%20truth%3A%20that%20Israel%20had%20been%20manipulating%2C%20had%20been%20executing%2C%20had%20been%20practising%20apartheid%20and%20occupation%20against%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20for%2075%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20crimes%2C%20under%20international%20law%2C%20under%20humanitarian%20international%20law%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20all%E2%80%A6%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20really%20interpret%20things%20or%20to%20be%20clever%20about%20it.%20Doesn%E2%80%99t%20really%20take%20a%20genius%20to%20discover%20that%20the%20Israeli%20military%20occupation%20had%20been%2C%20you%20know%2C%20targeting%20every%20Pale