e%20of%20the%20West%20Bank%20feel%20let%20down%20by%20the%20Palestine%20Authority%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDI%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Let%20me%20put%20it%20this%20way.%20There%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20trust%2C%20yes%2C%20between%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20and%20the%20PNA%20%5BPalestine%20Authority%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20again%2C%20because%20the%20PNA%20and%20the%20PLO%20had%20promised%20us%20independence%2C%20state%2C%20sovereignty%20and%20dignity%20to%20say%20the%20least%2C%20yet%20we%20did%20not%20get%20anything.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20I%20think%20the%20Israelis%20and%20the%20international%20community%20had%20led%20and%20had%20you%20know%20trapped%20the%20PLO%20and%20the%20PNA%20into%20this%20point%20where%20the%20PLO%20and%20the%20Palestinian%20leadership%20had%20lost%20the%20trust%20of%20their%20own%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Let%E2%80%99s%20come%20back%20for%20a%20moment%20to%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDo%20you%20have%20any%20sense%20of%20how%20popular%20Hamas%20is%20in%20Gaza%20today%3F%20We%20are%20often%20told%20by%20international%20statesmen%20that%20Hamas%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20represent%20all%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza.%20But%20what%20percentage%20of%20Gazans%20support%20Hamas%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDI%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Okay.%20Well%2C%20Gaza%20is%20about%202.2%20million%20civilians.%20Those%20people%20want%20to%20live%20in%20dignity%20and%20peace.%20Those%20people%2C%20the%202%20million%20people%2C%20half%20of%20them%20are%20children!%20Half%20of%20them%20are%20children%2C%20so%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20Hamas%20is.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%2C%20you%20know%2C%20even%20the%20right%20of%20resistance%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20what%20needs%20to%20be%20made%20very%20clear%20to%20your%20audiences%20in%20India.%201.1%20million%20of%20that%20population%20are%20children%20who%20don%E2%80%99t%20understand%20politics.%20So%20this%20messaging%20is%20very%20misleading%