ng%20and%20this%20settler%20colonial%20project%20has%20been%20ongoing.%20This%20%5Bwar%20of%20late%5D%20is%20being%20framed%20as%20an%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20because%20this%20is%20a%20logical%20argument%20that%20they%20could%20convince%20audiences%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20reality%20they%20are%20using%20this%20pretext%2C%20they%20are%20using%20Hamas%20as%20a%20fig%20leaf%2C%20but%20their%20target%20is%20Gaza%2C%20is%20the%20land%2C%20is%20to%20evict%20the%20Palestinian%20people%2C%20is%20to%20continue%20to%20annex%20the%20land%20as%20part%20of%20their%20settler%20colonial%20project%20which%20will%20continue%20also%20in%20the%20West%20Bank.%20They%20are%20hoping%20that%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20will%20be%20evicted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20why%20the%20Jordanian%20and%20the%20Egyptian%20position%2C%20which%20might%20sound%20a%20little%20bit%20inhumane%20in%20face%20of%20the%20sufferings%20of%20the%20millions%20of%20civilians%2C%20but%20on%20the%20political%20level%20we%20need%20to%20realise%20that%20they%20are%20saving%20the%20Palestinian%20national%20project%2C%20which%20is%20part%20of%20the%20deal%20of%20the%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20why%20we%20see%20the%20USA%2C%20the%20shuttle%20diplomacy%20from%20Blinken%20and%20Biden%20providing%20this%20legal%20coverage%20for%20the%20Israeli%20war%20crimes%20against%20the%20Palestinian%20people%2C%20it%20is%20basically%20to%20serve%20their%20interests%20in%20their%20electoral%20campaigns%20coming%20soon%2C%20and%20for%20the%20right-wing%20leaders%2C%20of%20course%2C%20in%20Europe%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20also%2C%20because%20this%20is%20a%20pragmatic%20scenario%20of%20a%20win-win%2C%20a%20cake%20sharing%20scenario%20for%20the%20Israel%2C%20the%20US%20and%20many%20other%20regional%20players%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20national%20rights%2C%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20right%20to%20self-determination%2C%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20the%20li