ty%2C%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20anymore%20to%20have%20a%20Palestinian%20state%2C%20given%20all%20the%20settlements%2C%20the%20divisions%2C%20and%20given%20all%20the%20military%20system%2C%20that%20is%20the%20occupation%20system%2C%20that%20is%20entrenched%2C%20that%20is%20hindering%20any%20possibility%20for%20the%20Palestinian%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELet%20alone%20Netanyahu%20and%20his%20leaders%20and%20his%20government%E2%80%99s%20statements%20of%20saying%20no%20to%20Palestinian%20state.%20The%20fact%20that%20they%20are%20saying%20no%20to%20a%20Palestinian%20state%2C%20no%20to%20peace%20talks%2C%20no%20to%20negotiations%2C%20make%20us%20have%20%E2%80%93%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20wishful%20scenario%20of%20having%20a%20one-state%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhy%20would%20I%20say%20no%20to%20a%20one%20state%20reality%2C%20if%20I%20want%20to%20honour%20civilians%2C%20if%20I%20want%20to%20honour%20humanity%2C%20if%20I%20want%20to%20end%20the%20sufferings%20of%20the%20millions%20of%20Palestinian%20people%20under%20the%20Israeli%20military%20occupation%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20under%20equal%20rights%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20an%20apartheid%20state.%20The%20fact%20that%20Israel%20is%20trying%20to%20export%20what%20is%20happening%20here%20as%20a%20religious%20issue%20has%20led%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Israelis%20will%20not%20accept%20a%20one-state%20%5Bsolution%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBecause%20this%20is%20not%20a%20Jewish-Muslim%20or%20a%20Jewish-Muslim-Christian%20conflict.%20No%2C%20it%20is%20a%20conflict%20over%20land.%20It%20is%20a%20settler%20colonial%20project.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20problem%20with%20the%20Jews.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYou%20know%2C%20I%20have%20many%20Jewish%20friends%20all%20around%20the%20world%2C%20I%20studied%20with%20many%20of%20them%2C%20I%20have%20colleagues%2C%20many%20of%20them%2C%20and%20I%20keep%20good%2C%20positive%20and%20healthy%20relationships%20with%20many%20of%20them.%20Those%20who%20are%20enlightened%2C%20those%20who%20are%20in%20education%2C%20those%20who%20believe%20in%20me%20as%20an%20equal%20citizen.%20This%20is%20the%20message%20that%20we%20need%20to%20realise.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20Dalal%20Iriqat%20in%20Palestine%2C%20and%20Shlomo%20in%20Tel%20Aviv%20or%20Herzliya%2C%20or%20Ahmed%20in%20Pakistan%20or%20in%20India%20or%20in%20New%20York%20or%20in%20Paris%20or%20in%20Shanghai%20or%20in%20Greenland%2C%20are%20seen%20as%20equal%20human%20beings%2C%20then%20we%20will%20not%20look%20at%20the%20shape%20of%20the%20solution%20but%20we%20will%20look%20for%20humanity%20and%20for%20justice%20for%20every%20civilian%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20it%20is%20Muslim%2C%20Christian%2C%20Jewish%2C%20Buddhist%20or%20atheist.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20message%20that%20we%20need%20to%20hear%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Palestinians%20are%20not%20being%20treated%20or%20viewed%20by%20the%20Western%20media%20as%20equal%20citizens%20who%20are%20entitled%20to%20equal%20universal%20human%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Dr%20Iriqat%2C%20thank%20you%20very%20much%20for%20the%20time%20you%20have%20given%20me%20and%20thank%20you%20very%20much%20for%20explaining%20in%20detail%20what%20it%20is%20like%20to%20be%20Palestinian%20in%20Israel.%20Take%20care%2C%20stay%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDI%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Thank%20you%20very%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698324041000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26153746%2Fkt-23-oct-sec-b-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Ffull-text-karan-thapar-interview-dala-iriqat-palestine%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Palestinian%20professor%20Dalal%20Iriqat%20pointed%20out%20that%20%E2%80%93%20among%20other%20things%20%E2%80%93%20Israel%20withdrew%20from%20Gaza%20in%202005%20but%20continues%20to%20exert%20significant%20control%20over%20what%20enters%20and%20leaves%20the%20strip%2C%20and%20that%20Hamas%20is%20not%20the%20only%20one%