%2C%20Gaza%E2%80%99s%20health%20ministry%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fenglish.alarabiya.net%2FNews%2Fmiddle-east%2F2023%2F10%2F25%2FMinistry-At-least-6-546-including-2-704-children-killed-in-Israeli-strikes-on-Gaza%5C%22%3Eissued%20a%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20of%20the%206%2C546%20Palestinians%20who%20had%20been%20killed%20in%20Israeli%20air%20strikes%20so%20far%2C%202%2C704%20were%20children.%20Images%20of%20the%20hunched%20shoulders%20of%20male%20volunteers%2C%20cradling%20tiny%20forms%20in%20their%20arms%2C%20point%20to%20the%20new%20architecture%20of%20loss%2C%20matching%20the%20bombed%20landscape%20that%20Israel%20has%20willed%20with%20impunity%20in%20Gaza.%20Moreover%2C%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20act%20of%20cutting%20off%20water%2C%20electricity%2C%20food%20and%20fuel%20supplies%2C%20which%20is%20against%20international%20law%2C%20has%20given%20rise%20to%20an%20unprecedented%20humanitarian%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHandala%20Tells%20Tales%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20children%20of%20Gaza%20have%20been%20forsaken%20by%20imperious%20western%20powers%20that%20want%20the%20world%20to%20think%20of%20Israeli%20bombs%20raining%20down%20on%20their%20fragile%20bodies%20as%20just%20punishment.%20But%20there%20is%20one%20figure%20%E2%80%93%20fittingly%2C%20a%20child%2C%20a%20boy%20%E2%80%93%20who%20promises%20to%20be%20a%20witness%20to%20the%20young%20ones%E2%80%99%20suffering%20caused%20by%20each%20successive%20strike.%20In%20fact%2C%20this%20child%20has%20been%20a%20steadfast%20witness%20to%20the%20history%20of%20dispossession%20that%20has%20marked%20Palestinians%20in%20over%20five%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20174px)%2085vw%2C%20174px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26165334%2FFig.1.Handala-594x1024-1-174x300.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22174%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2