EWho%20was%20Sherika%20De%20Armas%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20model%20represented%20Uruguay%20at%20the%20international%20level%20in%202015.%20At%20the%20competition%20in%20Sanya%2C%20China%2C%20she%20couldn't%20make%20it%20to%20the%20top%2030%2C%20but%20she%20was%20only%20among%20six%2018-year-olds%20at%20that%20time%20of%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20complimented%20for%20her%20%26quot%3Bbeautiful%20face%2C%20towering%20height%20and%20charismatic%20personality%26quot%3B%2C%20with%20one%20outlet%20calling%20Ms%20De%20Armas%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20young%20promising%20talents%20of%20Uruguay.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20always%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20model%2C%20whether%20a%20beauty%20model%2C%20an%20advertising%20model%20or%20a%20catwalk%20model%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20had%20told%20NetUruguay%20after%20the%202015%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20dangerous%20is%20cervical%20cancer%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%2C%20cervical%20cancer%20is%20the%20fourth%20most%20common%20cancer%20in%20women.%20The%20Clinical%20Oncology%20Society%20said%20that%20an%20estimated%20341%2C831%20women%20died%20from%20cervical%20cancer%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20cervical%20cancer%20usually%20spreads%20in%20four%20ways%3A%20From%20cervix%20to%20the%20uterus%2C%20outside%20the%20cervix%20or%20uterus%20but%20is%20detected%20before%20reaching%20the%20walls%20of%20the%20pelvis%2C%20reaching%20lower%20part%20of%20the%20vagina%2C%20and%20finally%20to%20the%20lining%20of%20the%20bladder%2C%20the%20rectum%2C%20or%20to%20distant%20organs%20and%20bones%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.healthline.com%2Fhealth%2Fcervical-cancer%2Fcan-you-die-from-cervical-cancer%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHealthline%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbout%20the%20new%20treatment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fhealth-67192441%5C%22%3EThe%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20250%20women%20with%20cervical%20cancer%20received%20the%20new%20treatment%20-%20an%20intensive%20six-week%20course%20of%20carboplatin%20and%20paclitaxel%20chemotherapy%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20%26quot%3Busual%26quot%3B%20treatment%20of%20radiotherapy%20plus%20weekly%20cisplatin%20and%20brachytherapy%2C%20known%20as%20chemoradiation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20gave%20another%20group%20of%20250%20women%20-%20known%20as%20the%20control%20group%20-%20the%20usual%20chemoradiation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20five%20years%2C%2080%20per%20cent%20of%20those%20who%20had%20received%20the%20new%20treatment%20were%20alive%20and%2073%20per%20cent%20had%20not%20seen%20their%20cancer%20return%20or%20spread.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20control%20group%2C%2072%20per%20cent%20were%20alive%20and%2064%20per%20cent%20had%20not%20seen%20their%20cancer%20return%20or%20spread.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20trial%20shows%20that%20this%20short%20course%20of%20additional%20chemotherapy%20delivered%20immediately%20before%20the%20standard%20CRT%20can%20reduce%20the%20risk%20of%20the%20cancer%20returning%20or%20death%20by%2035%20per%20cent.%20This%20is%20the%20biggest%20improvement%20in%20outcome%20in%20this%20disease%20in%20over%2020%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Mary%20McCormack%2C%20lead%20investigator%20of%20the%20trial%20from%20UCL%20Cancer%20Institute%20and%20UCLH%2C%20told%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698321240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fag6eglhg_shey-de-armas-_625x300_16_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsherika-de-armas-former-miss-world-contestant-from-uruguay-died-of-cervical-cancer-days-later-a-medical-breakthrough-4516243%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20new%20breakthrough%20led%20to%20drug%20advance%20never%20seen%20before%20in%2020%20years.%20It%20was%20based%20on%20the%20results%20of%20a%20study%20that%20continued%20for%205%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsherika-de-armas-former-miss-world-contestant-from-uruguay-died-of-cervical-cancer-days-later-a-medical-breakthrough-4516243%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsherika-de-armas-former-miss-world-contestant-from-uruguay-died-of-cervical-cancer-days-later-a-medical-breakthrough-4516243%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsherika-de-armas-former-miss-world-contestant-from-uruguay-died-of-cervical-cancer-days-later-a-medical-breakthrough-4516243%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Suhana%20told%20Zoya%3A%20Don't%20freak%20out%20if%20I%20fall%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698320580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104729281%2Cimgsize-31306.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fthe-archies-suhana-khan-asked-zoya-akhtar-to-not-freak-out-if-she-fell-while-skating%2Farticleshow%2F104729337.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104729337.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESuhana%20Khan%2C%20set%20to%20debut%20in%20Zoya%20Akhtar's%20%26quot%3BThe%20Archies%2C%26quot%3B%20shared%20her%20experience%20of%20learning%20to%20skate%20for%20the%20film%2C%20including%20falls%20and%20bumps.%20She%20emphasized%20the%20film's%20importance%20as%20a%20newcomer's%20training%20ground.%20Suhana%20is%20rumored%20to%20collaborate%20with%20her%20father%2C%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%2C%20in%20a%20Sujoy%20Ghosh%20thriller%20after%20this%20project.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofi