0positive%20to%20negative.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698320220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-05%2Femail-generic_650x400_81462519153.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Funusual-email-exchange-between-indian-student-and-german-professor-goes-viral-4516184%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20screenshot%2C%20the%20student%20can%20be%20seen%20introducing%20himself%20and%20submitting%20his%20application%20for%20the%20internship.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Funusual-email-exchange-between-indian-student-and-german-professor-goes-viral-4516184%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Funusual-email-exchange-between-indian-student-and-german-professor-goes-viral-4516184%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Funusual-email-exchange-between-indian-student-and-german-professor-goes-viral-4516184%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mohan%20Bhagwat%E2%80%99s%20Comments%20on%20Manipur%20Violence%20Show%20Northeast%20Remains%20a%20Puzzle%20That%20RSS%20Can%E2%80%99t%20Solve%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26164920%2FF9LZj2qaAAAgrSt.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20On%20October%2024%2C%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20supremo%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%20squarely%20blamed%20%E2%80%98external%20forces%E2%80%99%20for%20the%20Manipur%20violence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuch%20as%20it%20matches%20the%20stand%20taken%20by%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20governments%20at%20the%20Centre%20and%20in%20Manipur%2C%20it%2C%20nevertheless%2C%20comes%20off%20as%20a%20strident%20attempt%20at%20narrative%20correction%20by%20the%20top%20Hindutva%20leader%20%E2%80%93%20perhaps%20to%20garb%20the%20right-wing%20outfit%E2%80%99s%20own%20powerlessness%20in%20the%20Northeast.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESoon%20after%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20broke%20out%20in%20Manipur%20on%20May%203%2C%20the%20narrative%20in%20both%20local%20and%20national%20media%20was%20set.%20It%20broke%20out%20during%20a%20tribal%20solidarity%20march%20carried%20out%20in%20all%20hill%20districts%20of%20the%20state%20against%20the%20Manipur%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20order%20to%20the%20state%20government%20that%20it%20should%20recommend%20the%20inclusion%20of%20the%20Meitei%20community%20in%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(ST)%20list.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20quick%20succession%2C%20we%20saw%20the%20line%20shifting%20to%20%E2%80%98narco-terrorism%E2%80%99%2C%20allegedly%20by%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%E2%80%9D%20Kukis.%20It%20was%20particularly%20vented%20not%20just%20by%20the%20Meitei-faction%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20state%20but%20also%20the%20Sangh%20%3Cem%3Eparivar%3C%2Fem%3E%20across%20the%20country.%20Peddling%20of%20drugs%20within%20the%20state%2C%20and%20from%20outside%20the%20international%20border%2C%20has%20been%20a%20matter%20of%20concern%20not%20just%20in%20Manipur%20but%20in%20some%20other%20northeastern%20states%20too.%20However%2C%20in%20a%20state%20where%20the%20incumbent%20chief%20minister%20was%20once%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fformer-manipur-asp-thounaojam-brinda-details-how-biren-singh-pressured-her-to-drop-2018-drug-case%5C%22%3Eaccused%20by%20a%20police%20officer%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20an%20affidavit%20in%20the%20high%20court%20for%20asking%20her%20to%20%E2%80%9Cgo%20slow%E2%80%9D%20on%20a%20drug%20kingpin%20(from%20the%20Kuki%20community)%2C%20it%20was%20only%20a%20matter%20of%20time%20before%20that%20narrative%20lost%20steam.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELo%20and%20behold%2C%20it%20did.%20None%20other%20than%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20began%20telling%20select%20local%20and%20national%20media%20outlets%20that%20%E2%80%98external%20forces%E2%80%99%20infiltrating%20Manipur%20through%20the%20open%20border%20with%20strife-torn%20Myanmar%20piloted%20the%20violence%20that%20left%20hundreds%20dead%20and%20injured%20and%20displaced%20at%20least%2070%2C000%20people%20belonging%20to%20both%20Kuki%20and%20Meitei%20communities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20same%20narrative%20was%20mouthed%20by%20Bhagwat%20at%20his%20annual%20Vijayadashami%20address%20to%20the%20cadres%20at%20the%20RSS%20headquarters%20in%20Nagpur.%20The%20Hindutva%20ideologue%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frss-chief-mohan-bhagwat-how-did-manipur-violence-continue-unabated-despite-a-strong-government%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EWhy%2C%20and%20by%20whom%2C%20was%20an%20attempt%20made%20to%20give%20a%20communal%20tinge%20to%20this%20mutual%20conflict%20between%20the%20Manipuri%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20communities%2C%20who%20were%20apprehensive%20about%20the%20future%20of%20their%20existence%3F%20Who%20has%20a%20vested%20interest%20in%20trying%20to%20drag%20and%20besmirch%20an%20organisation%20like%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%2C%20which%20has%20been%20engaged%20in%20serving%20everyone%20without%20any%20bias%20for%20years%2C%20into%20this%20unfortunate%20incident%20without%20any%20reason%3F%20Which%20foreign%20powers%20may%20be%20interested%20in%20taking%20advantage%20of%20such%20unrest%20and%20instability%20in%20Manipur%2C%20located%20between%20Nagabhoomi%20and%20Mizoram%20in%20this%20border%20area%3F%20Does%20the%20geopolitics%20of%20Southeast%20Asia%20also%20have%20a%20role%20in%20these%20events%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20utterance%20came%20across%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20separate%20the%20RSS%20from%20the%20Manipur%20violence%2C%20perhaps%20because%20local%20rightwing%20outfits%20with%20alleged%20links%20to%20it%20%E2%80%93%20like%20the%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20and%20Meitei%20Leepun%20%E2%80%93%20were%20widely%20alleged%20to%20have%20a%20hand%20in%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20Kukis%20in%20the%20valley%20areas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMore%20importantly%2C%20Bhagwat%E2%80%99s%20words%20miss%20a%20peculiar%20element%20within%20societies%20across%20the%20Northeast%2C%20which%20organisations%20like%20the%20RSS%2C%20hinged%20on%20religious%20hegemony%2C%20find%20hard%20to%20crack.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAcross%20large%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20caste%20and%20religion%20can%20play%20a%20determining%20role%20in%20huddling%20a%20society%20under%20one%20umbrella.%20In%20the%20northeastern%20belt%2C%20what%20cements%20a%20group%20of%20people%20as%20one%20is%20the%20strong%20sense%20of%20community.%20Pluck%20out%20from%20recent%20history%20any%20bloody%20strife%20that%20rocked%20the%20region%20and%20you%20will%20find%20that%20fear%20of%20one%20community%20losing%20its%20power%20to%20another%20is%20at%20its%20root.%20Not%20religion%20or%20caste.%20It%20is%20this%20strong%20sense%20of%20community%20that%20gives%20agency%20to%20any%20grouping%20of%20people%20across%20the%20region%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20a%20majority%20or%20minority.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20factor%20was%20seen%20playing%20out%20in%20the%20Kuki-Meitei%20clashes%20too.%20Kukis%20may%20be%20a%20minority%20in%20Manipur%20but%20are%20certainly%20not%20voiceless%3B%20not%20cowering%20against%20a%20community%20which%20is%20in%20greater%20numbers%20in%20their%20state%20and%20also%20has%20in%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20a%20chief%20minister%20perceived%20as%20batting%20only%20for%20his%20Meitei%20community.%20The%20agency%20required%20to%20put%20up%20a%20fight%20was%20drawn%20from%20the%20neighbouring%20Mizos%2C%20their%20kindred%20tribe.%20Mizoram%20chief%20minister%20Zoramthanga%20soon%20acted%20as%20the%20equivalent%20of%20Biren%20Singh%20for%20the%20Kukis%20of%20Manipur.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20this%20sense%20of%20community%20that%20also%20kicks%20up%20a%20peculiarity%20during%20a%20riot%20or%20violent%20situation%20in%20the%20Northeast.%20While%20Church%20and%20Hindutva%20leaders%20were%20going%20all%20out%20in%20the%20media%2C%20counting%20the%20number%20of%20churches%20and%20temples%20burnt%20respectively%20during%20the%20Manipur%20violence%2C%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20Meitei%20Christians%20were%20accusing%20the%20Kuki%20Christians%20of%20setting%20fire%20to%20their%20churches.%20Clearly%2C%20then%2C%20religion%20appears%20to%20have%20played%20a%20subservient%20role%20to%20the%20sense%20of%20community.%20If%20those%20accusations%20were%20true%2C%20Meitei%20Christians%20were%20lumped%20in%20by%20the%20Kukis%20with%20the%20Meities%20who%20are%20Vaishnavites%20and%20followers%20of%20Sanamahism.%20Ditto%20the%20case%20with%20some%20recent%20attacks%20against%20the%20Meitei%20Pangals%20or%20Muslims%20in%20the%20Kwakta%20area%20that%20borders%20the%20Kuki-dominated%20Churachandpur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26164931%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-26-at-4.45.57-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26164931%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-26-at-4.45.57-PM.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26164931%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-26-at-4.45.57-PM-300x134.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26164931%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-26-at-4.45.57-PM-1024x457.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681879%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22536%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20protest%20in%20Manipur%20against%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Meitei%20pangal%20man.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20small%20section%20within%20the%20Kukis%20is%20Bnei%20Menashe%2C%20or%20Jewish.%20Wilson%20Hangshing%2C%20an%20MLA%20and%20co-founder%20of%20the%20Kuki%20People%E2%80%99s%20Alliance%2C%20who%20has%20been%20an%20important%20voice%20in%20the%20national%20media%20for%20the%20Kukis%20during%20the%20Manipur%20clash%2C%20belongs%20to%20that%20community.%20But%20religious%20identity%20was%20never%20a%20factor%20when%20it%20came%20to%20joining%20hands%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20Kukis%2C%20who%20are%20mostly%20Christian.%20It%20is%20also%20this%20sense%20of%20community%20and%20kinship%20that%20pivots%20the%20Mizoram%20government%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20of%20orders%20from%20New%20Delhi%20to%20push%20back%20the%20Chin%20refugees%20into%20Myanmar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%201983%20Nellie%20riots%20of%20Assam%20too%2C%20the%20sense%20of%20community%20played%20out.%20Multiple%20instances%20of%20violence%20were%20noted%20where%20villagers%20attacked%20villagers%20from%20other%20communities.%20E.%20Rammohan%2C%20who%20was%20an%20Assam%20police%20officer%20then%2C%20notes%20in%20his%20book%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESimply%20Khaki%3A%20A%20Policeman%20Remembers%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ethat%20a%20group%20of%20Assamese%20Muslims%20attacked%20Muslims%20of%20East%20Bengal%20origin%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Darrang%20district.%20Clearly%2C%20then%20too%2C%20community%20was%20the%20pivot.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20all-so-common%20insider-outsider%20conflicts%20that%20break%20out%20across%20the%20Northeast%2C%20religion%20more%20often%20than%20not%20takes%20a%20backseat%20when%20posed%20against%20the%20idea%20of%20community.%20Take%20the%20Chakmas%20of%20Arunachal%20Pradesh.%20They%20may%20be%20Buddhist%2C%20like%20a%20section%20of%20people%20in%20the%20state%2C%20but%20it%20is%20never%20a%20concession%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20counting%20who%20comes%20under%20the%20umbrella%20of%20Arunachalee%20as%20a%20whole.%20The%20BJP-RSS%20have%20a%20strong%20base%20in%20both%20the%20Chakma%20and%20Arunachalee%20communities%2C%20but%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20bring%20them%20under%20one%20umbrella%20even%20after%20years%20of%20work.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20recent%20times%2C%20when%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRC)%20was%20being%20updated%20in%20Assam%20under%20the%20BJP%2C%20religious%20polarisation%20of%20the%20society%20was%20seen%20to%20be%20at%20its%20peak.%20That%20the%20state%20has%20a%20considerable%20population%20of%20Muslims%20of%20Bengali%20origin%20has%20helped%20matters%20for%20both%20Hindu%20and%20Islamic%20forces%20to%20blow%20their%20trumpets.%20However%2C%20by%20the%20time%20the%20Union%20government%20brought%20in%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%2C%20the%20old%20equations%20came%20to%20the%20fore.%20Firm%20lines%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fwe-are-protesting-as-assamese-not-as-hindu-or-muslim-anti-caa-agitators%2Farticleshow%2F72686245.cms%5C%22%3Edivision%20were%20drawn%3C%2Fa%3E%20not%20as%20per%20religion%20but%20community.%20Much%20as%20the%20BJP-RSS%20and%20chief%20minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20kept%20prodding%20the%20Assamese%20community%20to%20%E2%80%98identify%20the%20enemy%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20Bangladeshi%20Hindus%20found%20no%20acceptance.%20The%20religious%20card%20was%20thrown%20by%20the%20wayside%20when%20Guwahati%20saw%20a%20large%20crowd%20of%20anti-CAA%20protesters%20hitting%20the%20roads%2C%20mouthing%20the%2017%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20century%20Sufi%20saint%20Azan%20Fakir%E2%80%99s%20Jikir%2C%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20or%20Muslim%2C%20we%20are%20the%20children%20of%20the%20same%20god%E2%80%A6%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26164434%2FCitizenship_Amendment_Act_protests_in_Guwahati.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26164434%2FCitizenship_Amendment_Act_protests_in_Guwahati.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26164434%2FCitizenship_Amendment_Act_protests_in_Guwahati-300x167.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681876%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22571%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20protest%20in%20Guwahati%20against%20the%20CAA.%20Photo%3A%20Dr%20Vikramjit%20Kakati%2FWikimedia%20Commons%2C%20CC%20BY-SA%204.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20has%20uncanny%20similarities%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98Assam%20problem%E2%80%99%20of%20the%201980s%20%E2%80%93%20the%20bogey%20of%20%E2%80%98illegal%20immigrants%E2%80%99.%20Even%20then%2C%20there%20is%20a%20variation.%20In%20Assam%2C%20a%20sub-nationalist%20movement%20led%20by%20the%20majority%20Assamese%20community%20began%20tilting%20towards%20religion%20(read%20Hindu)%20in%20later%20decades%20(until%20the%20anti-CAA%20movement%20against%20accepting%20Hindu%20Bangladeshis%20in%20Assam%20broke%20that%20continuity).%20In%20Manipur%20though%2C%20it%20began%20as%20a%20religious%20assertion%20with%20the%20involvement%20of%20groups%20like%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20and%20Meitei%20Leepun%20but%20is%20now%20gradually%20leaning%20towards%20an%20assertion%20of%20Meitei%20sub-nationalism.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20a%20sense%20of%20community%20overrides%20that%20of%20religion.%20For%20outfits%20structured%20around%20religiou