20He%20will%20join%20on%20January%201%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVaswani%E2%80%99s%20selection%20was%20unexpected%2C%20as%20the%20media%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fwhole-time-directors-seen-to-succeed-kotak-at-bank%2Farticleshow%2F103335821.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20shortlisting%20of%20two%20internal%20candidates%20for%20RBI%E2%80%99s%20approval.%20They%20were%20K.P.S.%20Manian%2C%20head%20of%20corporate%2C%20institutional%20and%20investment%20banking%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kotak.com%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2FKotak%2Fabout-us%2Fexecutive-board%2FKotak_Shanti_Ekambaram%2520_Profile.pdf%5C%22%3EShanti%20Ekambaram%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20head%20of%20consumer%20banking.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPrakash%20Apte%2C%20chairman%20of%20KMB%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kotak.com%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2FKotak%2Fabout-us%2Fmedia-press-releases%2F2023%2FCEO-Appointment-Final.pdf%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20pleased%20to%20announce%20that%20%5Bthe%5D%20RBI%20has%20approved%20the%20appointment%20of%20Ashok%20Vaswani%20as%20the%20next%20MD%20and%20CEO%20of%20KMB.%20Ashok%20is%20a%20global%20banking%20leader%20with%20a%20proven%20track%20record%20of%20building%20and%20growing%20businesses%20at%20an%20international%20scale%20and%20has%20successfully%20steered%20organisations%20to%20greater%20heights.%20We%20are%20confident%20that%20Ashok%20will%20accelerate%20change%20and%20drive%20growth%20at%20Kotak.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUday%20Kotak%2C%20founder%20and%20director%2C%20KMB%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fudaykotak%2Fstatus%2F1715663361277296851%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0%E2%80%9CI%20am%20delighted%20that%20the%20RBI%20has%20approved%20our%20recommendation%2C%20Ashok%20Vaswani%2C%20as%20the%20next%20CEO%20of%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Bank.%20Ashok%20is%20a%20world%20class%20leader%20and%20banker%20with%20digital%20and%20customer%20focus.%20I%20am%20proud%20that%20we%20bring%20a%20%E2%80%98Global%20Indian%E2%80%99%20home%20to%20build%20Kotak%20and%20India%20of%20tomorrow.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Fhigh-attrition-rate-at-kotak-mahindra-bank-fails-to-find-a-spot-in-annual-report%5C%22%3EThe%20Issue%20of%20High%20Attrition%20Rate%20at%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Bank%20Fails%20to%20Find%20a%20Spot%20in%20Annual%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIgnoring%20internal%20talent%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETypically%2C%20successful%20organisations%20take%20pride%20in%20grooming%20CEOs%20from%20within.%20The%20board%E2%80%99s%20Nomination%20and%20Remuneration%20Committee%20is%20responsible%20for%20nurturing%20internal%20talent%20for%20leadership%20succession%2C%20especially%20for%20strategic%20posts%20such%20as%20the%20post%20of%20the%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20Aditya%20Puri%20retired%20from%20HDFC%20Bank%2C%20Sashi%20Jagdishan%20(then%2056%20years%20of%20age)%2C%20a%20senior%20HDFC%20Bank%20executive%2C%20succeeded%20him.%20In%20ICICI%20Bank%2C%20after%20Chanda%20Kochhar%20was%20sacked%20by%20the%20board%2C%20Sandeep%20Bakshi%20(then%2058%20years)%2C%20a%20long-serving%20ICICI%20Bank%20senior%20executive%2C%20was%20appointed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20in%20the%20case%20of%20banks%20in%20which%20outside%20candidates%20replaced%20the%20CEOs%2C%20it%20was%20either%20because%20the%20banks%20were%20facing%20some%20serious%20issues%20and%20internal%20candidates%20were%20regarded%20as%20being%20part%20of%20the%20problem%2C%20or%20because%20the%20RBI%20lacked%20confidence%20in%20the%20internal%20candidates%20recommended%20by%20the%20board.%20Such%20were%20the%20cases%20in%20Axis%20Bank%2C%20when%20Amitabh%20Chaudhry%20(then%2055%20years)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Faxis-bank-appoints-amitabh-chaudhry-as-md-and-ceo-