e%20are%20no%20innocent%20civilians%20in%20Gaza%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20justification%20is%20the%20language%20of%20violence.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20western%20world%20very%20well%20recognises%20the%20impact%20of%20language%20and%20the%20sheer%20violence%20it%20can%20unleash.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20call%20the%20current%20bombing%20and%20brutality%20in%20Gaza%20a%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewar%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20between%20Palestine%20and%20Israel%20is%20to%20trivialise%20the%20injustices%20of%20the%20Israeli%20regime.%20It%20dilutes%20the%20indisputable%20fact%20that%20Israel%20is%20illegally%20and%20violently%20in%20occupation%20of%20Palestinian%20territory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19124105%2Fgazarimal_2023-10-18_195802-1024x392.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19124105%2Fgazarimal_2023-10-18_195802-1024x392.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19124105%2Fgazarimal_2023-10-18_195802-300x115.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19124105%2Fgazarimal_2023-10-18_195802.png%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680776%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22322%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDestruction%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%20Photo%3A%20UNICEF%2FHassan%20Islyeh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Nazi%20minister%20for%20propaganda%20and%20public%20enlightenment%2C%20Joseph%20Goebbels%20once%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CPropaganda%20is%20absolutely%20necessary%2C%20even%20if%20it%20is%20only%20a%20means%20to%20an%20end.%20Otherwise%2C%20the%20idea%20could%20never%20take%20over%20the%20state.%20I%20must%20be%20able%20to%20get%20what%20I%20think%20is%20important%20across%20many%20people.%E2%80%9D%20In%20other%20words%2C%20no%20narrative%20is%20useful%20till%20it%20is%20accepted%20by%20a%20section%20of%20the%20population.%20It%20does%20not%20astonish%20me%20anymore%20that%20a%20big%20chunk%20of%20the%20Indian%C2%A0%20media%20and%20social%20media%20universe%20continues%20to%20participate%20whole%20heartedly%20in%20the%20buildup%20and%20sustenance%20of%20the%20Israeli%20narrative%20surrounding%20this%20crisis.%20There%20are%20the%20same%20people%20who%20support%20the%20Hindu%20nationalist%20regime%20in%20India.%20They%20see%20India%E2%80%99s%20stand%20in%20favour%20of%20Palestine%20in%20the%20past%20as%20an%20attempt%20by%20previous%20regimes%20to%20%E2%80%98appease%E2%80%99%20Indian%20Muslims.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPernicious%20hatred%20for%20Muslims%20is%20the%20glue%20which%20binds%20them%20with%20the%20Israeli%20narrative.%20They%20fail%20to%20realise%20that%20the%20Palestine-Israel%20problem%20is%20not%20an%20exclusively%20Muslim-Jew%20issue.%20India%E2%80%99s%20historic%20support%20to%20Palestine%20was%20based%20on%20our%20commitment%20and%20continuum%20of%20the%20anti-colonial%20legacy%20of%20the%20freedom%20struggle.%20It%20was%20no%20more%20an%20attempt%20at%20%E2%80%98appeasement%E2%80%99%20of%20Indian%20Muslims%20than%20was%20India%E2%80%99s%20stand%20against%20apartheid%20in%20South%20Africa%20or%20its%20support%20for%20the%20national%20liberation%20struggles%20of%20other%20colonised%20people%20in%20Africa%20and%20Asia.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20official%20Israeli%20narrative%20is%20costing%20human%20lives%20in%20thousands.%20The%20Israeli%20state%20is%20out%20there%20avenging%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20with%20a%20brutality%20and%20force%20unknown%20even%20to%20its%20tormented%20victims.%20They%20believe%20they%20are%20bringing%20the%20culprits%20to%20%E2%80%98justice%E2%80%99%20without%20realising%20that%20the%20line%20between%20justice%20and%20revenge%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eis%20precariously%20thin.%20It%20is%20so%20thin%20that%20it%20becomes%20non-existent%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20careless.%20Revenge%20is%20the%20tool%20of%20the%20weak%20and%20the%20angry.%20Justice%20is%20never%20delivered%20in%20anger.%20It%20weighs%20evidence%20and%20situations%20in%20context%20of%20the%20crime.%20The%20evidence%20has%20always%20been%20against%20Israel%2C%20right%20from%20its%20wrongful%20inception%20in%201948.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20loss%20of%20a%20moral%20compass%20can%20plunge%20societies%20into%20a%20free%20fall%20of%20madness%20and%20brutality.%20Building%20up%20narratives%20that%20contribute%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20children%2C%20women%20and%20the%20elderly%20is%20murder%20with%20malice.%20Frantz%20Fanon%20once%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C..because%20quite%20simply%20it%20was%2C%20in%20more%20than%20one%20way%2C%20becoming%20impossible%20for%20them%20%5Bthe%20colonised%5D%20to%20breathe%E2%80%9D.%20Palestinians%20need%20to%20breathe.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EShah%20Alam%20Khan%20is%20a%20professor%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20Orthopaedics%2C%20All%20India%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%2C%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698306405000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25123525%2FF9O1QYgbQAARmyY.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fas-israel-kills-thousands-of-palestinian-civilians-we-need-to-pay-attention-to-the-language-of-war%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Building%20up%20narratives%20that%20contribute%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20children%2C%20women%20and%20the%20elderly%20is%20murder%20with%20malice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fas-israel-kills-thousands-of-palestinian-civilians-we-need-to-pay-attention-to-the-language-of-war%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Designer%20Anish%20Malpani%20of%20%E2%80%98Without%E2%80%99%20Turns%20Packets%20of%20Chips%20into%20Eyewear%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26124400%2FScreenshot-2023-10-26-at-12.43.01-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20From%20sunglasses%20to%20jewellery%20to%20metallic%20jackets%20%E2%80%93%20Pune-based%20designer%20Anish%20Malpani%20and%20his%20label%20%E2%80%98Without%E2%80%99%20used%20chip%20packets%20and%20other%20impossible-to-recycle%20plastics%20in%20almost%20every%20aspect%20of%20their%20designs%20at%20the%205th%20annual%20Circular%20Design%20Challenge%20(CDC)%20organised%20by%20R%7CElan%20TM%20in%20association%20with%20the%20United%20Nations%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECDC%20is%20India%E2%80%99s%20largest%20award%20for%20designers%20and%20entrepreneurs%20that%20recognises%20and%20promotes%20circularity%2C%20sustainability%20and%20innovation%20in%20the%20fashion%20and%20textile%20industries.%20The%20challenge%20culminated%20in%20a%20finale%20show%20at%20the%20UN%20House%20during%20Lakm%C3%A9%20Fashion%20Week%20in%20partnership%20with%20FDCI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMalpani%20was%20named%20the%20winner%20of%20the%20challenge%2C%20which%20went%20global%20for%20the%20first%20time%20this%20year.%20The%20runner-up%20of%20the%20competition%20was%20Felipe%20Fiallo%20from%20the%20European%20Union.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20so%20inspiring%20to%20see%20all%20of%20the%20innovation%20and%20the%20ability%20of%20creative%20artists%20to%20merge%20something%20like%20fashion%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20fun%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20identity%20and%20creativity%20%E2%80%94%20with%20sustainability%2C%E2%80%9D%20UN%20resident%20coordinator%20Shombi%20Sharp%20said%20at%20the%20finale%20show.%20%E2%80%9CTo%2