0value%20and%20use%20that%20to%20empower%20ways%20out%20of%20poverty.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20part%20of%20his%20design%2C%20the%20frames%20of%20Malpani%E2%80%99s%20glasses%20have%20a%20QR%20code%20inside%20which%20people%20can%20scan%20to%20see%20where%20the%20waste%20came%20from%20and%20the%20story%20of%20the%20waste%20picker.%20Malpani%20said%20it%20has%20been%20humbling%20to%20hear%20stories%20from%20waste%20pickers%20he%20works%20with%20and%20hopes%20to%20help%20break%20the%20cycle%20of%20the%20profession.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26124646%2FScreenshot-2023-10-26-at-12.46.26-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26124646%2FScreenshot-2023-10-26-at-12.46.26-PM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26124646%2FScreenshot-2023-10-26-at-12.46.26-PM-300x167.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26124646%2FScreenshot-2023-10-26-at-12.46.26-PM-1024x571.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681802%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22669%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAnish%20Malpani%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Without%E2%80%99%20brand%20sported%20sunglasses%20made%20of%20%E2%80%9Cimpossible-to-recycle%E2%80%9D%20plastics.%20Stylists%20Daniel%20Franklin%20and%20Karishma%20Shahani-Khan%20styled%20the%20models%20for%20the%20Circular%20Design%20Challenge%20finale%20show.%20Photo%3A%20Yasmeen%20Saadi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EGoing%20forward%2C%20Malpani%20said%20he%20aims%20to%20expand%20past%20sunglasses%20and%20use%20the%20versatility%20of%20the%20material%20to%20make%20more%20jewellery%20and%20accessories%20lik