nin%2C%20which%20helps%20sleep%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20must%20think%20how%20much%20of%20this%20is%20being%20followed%20by%20our%20generation%20today.%20The%20doctor%20jokes%20that%20his%20friend%20Saravana%20Kumar%20wakes%20up%20before%20sunrise%20only%20to%20watch%20his%20favourite%20hero%E2%80%99s%20first-day-first-show%20movie%20in%20the%20theatre.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20sleeping%20two%20hours%20before%20sunrise%20these%20days!%20All%20the%20phones%20before%20bed%20neutralise%20the%20effects%20of%20melatonin%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20let%20you%20sleep.%20We%20are%20also%20doing%20desk%20jobs%20without%20any%20movement.%20Try%20working%20and%20eating%20only%20between%20sunrise%20and%20sunset.%20This%20will%20help%20the%20circadian%20rhythm%20of%20the%20body.%20Have%20a%20winding%20routine%20post%20sunset%20and%20give%20rest%20to%20your%20body%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20advises.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Pal%20further%20urges%20everyone%20to%20lead%20a%20balanced%20life%20and%20not%20compromise%20on%20health.%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20make%20this%20too%20complicated.%20You%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20eat%20quinoa%20or%20expensive%20organic%20food.%20Just%20follow%20your%20ancestors%20and%20keep%20it%20simple%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202123px)%20100vw%2C%202123px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC07729_11zon-1698070642-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222123%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Pal%20imparts%20crucial%20medical%20information%20through%20his%20stand-up%20comedy%20shows%20worldwide.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC07729_11zon-1698070642-scaled.jpg%202123w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC07729_11zon-1698070642-249x300.jpg%20249w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.