20To%20see%20the%20river%20flowing%2C%20even%20if%20only%20in%20part%2C%20gave%20Nutanben%20and%20her%20team%20a%20spark%20of%20joy%20that%20only%20a%20few%20other%20things%20could%20manage!%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20is%20perhaps%20only%20joy%20and%20satisfaction%20for%20the%20NGO%20team%20working%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20it%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20a%20far%20better%20quality%20of%20life%20for%20the%20farmers%20and%20the%20community%20living%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELaxman%20Sawade%20was%20growing%20around%20five%20quintals%20of%20cotton%20every%20year%20on%20his%20seven%20acre%20farm%20and%20barely%20managing%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%20In%202013%2C%20he%20took%20the%20initiative%20of%20applying%20300%20trollies%20of%20silt%20on%20three%20acres%20of%20his%20land.%20Not%20only%20has%20his%20cotton%20output%20gone%20up%2C%20he%20is%20also%20growing%20grapes%20on%20his%20land%20since.%20Overall%2C%20his%20income%20has%20jumped%20to%20Rs%2015%20lakh%20a%20year%2C%20helping%20him%20build%20a%20better%20home%2C%20buy%202.5%20additional%20acres%20of%20land%2C%20a%20tractor%20and%20a%20motorbike.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20the%20notion%20that%20almost%20nothing%20brings%20more%20prosperity%20and%20hope%20than%20water%20security%20has%20been%20amply%20reinforced%20by%20Jalna.%20Devkate%20says%20that%20three%20new%20factories%20have%20come%20up%20in%20the%20area%2C%20including%20a%20water%20intensive%20sugarcane%20factory%2C%20leading%20to%20new%20employment%20opportunities%20in%20the%20district.%20In%20a%20region%20that%20has%20been%20bereft%20of%20almost%20any%20work%20opportunities%2C%20this%2C%20he%20argues%2C%20is%20what%20has%20helped%20bring%20in%20more%20and%20more%20takers%20for%20the%20ongoing%20efforts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20806px)%20100vw%2C%20806px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20170307_11344